\mt1 Jon Osirizir Akar Aghuim 
\is1 Akar Faragha Zuim 
\ip Jon Osirizir Akar Aghuir kam, a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Iesus a ‚ÄúGod…®n Akam, a gumazim…®n m…®n otogha iza en tong…®n iti.‚Äù Jon kamagh…®n ifonge, gumazamiziba bar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n Otarim Iesus…®n ikiam. Egh me kamagh…®n fogh suam, Iesus a Gumazir God ua me Iniasa M…®sevezim. Jon kamagh…®n fo, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itiba, me ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarir zurara itim iniam. Kamagh…®n an ak…®nafarir kam osiri. N…® Jon 20:31…®n gan. 
\ip Jon faragha e m…®keme, Akar Kam fom…®ra God ko iti. Egha g…®n Jon Iesus…®n mirakelbar eghaghanibar gun m…®gei. Ez…® e dar gan fogham, Iesus a Gumazir God ua e Iniasa M…®sevezim, a God…®n Otarim. Jon uaghan Iesus amizir mirakelbar akar m…®ngaribar e m…®keme. Ez…® e gumazamizir mabar gari, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikiava an g…®n zui. Ez…® marazi n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikian aghua. 
\ip Akar sapta 13-17…®n itiba, Iesus…®n apaniba d…®magarim…®n an suiragha a gamizir araziba, Jon a dagh eghari. D…®magarir kam, Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko ikia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuir av…®riba me gan…®ngi. Ez…® g…®n apaniba Iesus…®n suiragha a kot gat…®gha, egha a isa ter ighuvim…®n a gafu. Akar abuananam, Iesus mozim…®n ua d…®kaviz…®, an suren gumaziba an gani. Bizir e dughiar av…®ribar Jon…®n ak…®nafarim…®n garim, a kamak…®n, Iesus nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibar dabirabim…®n bizibar gara da isa akar is…®n zuim dav gei. Ez…® am…®nim…®n akam, ko d…®pam…®n akam, ko bret…®n akam, ko anganzangarim…®n akam, ko wain…®n temem…®n akam, ko sipsipbar garir gumazim…®n akam, d…®penim…®n tiarakam…®n akam, bizir kaba Jon…®n ak…®nafarim…®n aven iti. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Akam gumazim…®n m…®n otogha iza gumazamizibar tong…®n iti 
\mr (Sapta 1) 
\s1 Akar Ik…®r…®m…®rir Zurara Itim An…®dim, a gumazim…®n m…®n oto 
\p  
\v 1 Bar fom…®ra fom…®ra, biziba bar t…®ghar otivamin dughiam, Akam iti. Akar kam God ko iti, egha a uab…® God.  
\v 2 Bar fom…®ra fom…®ra Akam God ko iti. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Akar kam…®n, God biziba bar dar ingariz…®ma, da otifi. Ez…® bizitam tuavir igharazi tam…®n otozir puvat…®. Akam uab…® bizibagh amiz…®ma, da otifi.  
\v 4 Egha Akar kamra, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim…®n m…®ngarim. Ez…® ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarir kam, a uaghan gumazamiziba angazangarim me gan…®di.  
\v 5 Ez…® angazangarir kam a m…®tatem…®n isima, m…®tatem anevaraghava egha anemungezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® God gumazir mam amada, an ziam Jon.  
\v 7 An akam akunasa ize. An angazangarir kam…®n akam…®n gun m…®k…®mt…®ma, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra a baragh…®va egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam. A ingangarir kam damuasa ize.  
\v 8 Egha Jon uab…® angazangarir kam puvat…®. An angazangarir kam…®n akam…®n gun m…®k…®masa ize.  
\v 9 Ez…® angazangarir kam guizbang…®n angazangarim. Egha nguazir kam…®n izegha gumazamiziba bar angazangarim me gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 10 Akam nguazir kam…®n iti. An gavgavim…®n, God nguazir kam…®n ingari, ez…® nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 11 A uan nguibamra ghuz…®ma an anababa an aghuagha a inizir puvat…®.  
\v 12 Ez…® gumazamizir maba a ini, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ziam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a me gamiz…®ma me God…®n boribar m…®n otifi.  
\v 13 Me amebaba ko afeziabar ghuzibar otifi, o m…®karzibar ifongiam…®n, o gumazim…®n ifongiam…®n God…®n boribar otivizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. God uab…® me gamiz…®ma me an boribar otifi. 
\p  
\v 14 Akam uab…® gumazim…®n m…®n oto. A bar God…®n Otarir vam…®ra, ez…® God a gamiz…® a God…®n gavgavim ko angazangarim ini. Ez…® God anemadaz…®ma an en tong…®n iti. Ez…® e an gavgavim ko angazangarim…®n gani. Ez…® apangkuvim ko guiz…®n akam bar a giz…®fa. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Jon gumazir kam…®n gun me m…®gei. Egha pamten dia ghaze, ‚ÄúA gumazir kam, k…® faragha an gun ia m…®kemegha g…®fa. K…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazir nan g…®n izim, a bar fom…®ra iti, ez…® nan amebam g…®n na bate. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an gavgavim bar nan gavgavim gafira.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® apangkuvim bar a giz…®fa, ez…® a uan apangkuvim…®n a dughiar av…®ribar bar derav…®ra e gami.  
\v 17 Guizbang…®ra, Moses Osirizir Araziba, God e bagha da isa Moses gan…®ngiz…®, ez…® Moses e gan…®ngi. Ez…® God, Krais Iesus…®n aven apangkuvim ko guizbang…®n arazim en aka.  
\v 18 Gumazitam bar God…®n ganizir puvat…®. Ez…® kar God…®n Otarir vam…®ra, a uab…® God, egha a bar God…®n borogh…®ra iti. A uab…®ra God en aka. 
\s1 Jon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, an akam akuri 
\r (Matyu 3:1-12 ko Mak 1:7-8 ko Luk 3:15-17) 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Judan gumazir aruaba, me ofa gamir gumazir maba ko Livain gumazir maba amadaz…®, me Jerusalem ategha Jon bagha iza kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® tinara?‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® Jon bighav…®ra m…®g…®a akam modir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim puvat…®.‚Äù\f + \ft (1:20) Grigh…®n akam…®n, God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, me a d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúKrais.‚Äù\f* 
\v 21 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúN…® tinara? N…® ti Elaija, o?‚Äù Ez…® a m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® me m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ti God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kamra, e n…® m…®zuai.‚Äù Ez…® an akam ikara, ‚ÄúPuvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, me uam an azara, ‚ÄúN…® bar tinara? E ikarvazir aghuitam inigh mang…®va gumazir e amadaz…®bav k…®mam. N…® manmagh…®ra uab…® m…®gei?‚Äù  
\v 23 Ez…® Jon kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® gumazir kam…®n tiarim, 
\q2 k…® gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia egha kamagh…®n d…®a m…®gei, 
\q2 ‚ÄòIa Ekiam bagh tuavim ak…®r.‚Äô‚Äù 
\b  
\m (Kar akar God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia fom…®ra osirizim.) 
\p  
\v 24 Gumazir kaba, Farisiba me amangiz…® me ize.  
\v 25 Egha me kamagh…®n Jon azara, ‚ÄúN…® Gumazir God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezim puvat…®gh, egh n…® Elaija puvat…®gh, egh n…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam puvat…®gha, egha n…® tizim sua gumazamiziba rue?‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® Jon kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® d…®pam…®n me rue. Ez…® gumazir mam ian tong…®n iti, ia a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 27 A gumazir kam, a nan g…®n izi. K…® an dagarir asuabar beniba f…®ran ibura.‚Äù  
\v 28 Jon Betanin nguibam…®n ikia akar kam me m…®keme, nguibar kam Jordan…®n d…®pam…®n vong…®n iti. Danganir kam…®n Jon gumazamiziba rue. 
\s1 Iesus a God…®n Sipsip…®n Nguzim 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® am…®m…®zarakan Jon Iesus…®n garima an a bagha izi. Ez…® Jon kamagh…®n m…®gei. ‚ÄúIa munagh gan! Munar God…®n Sipsip…®n Nguzim. A nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadi!  
\v 30 A gumazir kam, k…® fom…®ra kamagh…®n an gun m…®keme, ‚ÄòGumazir nan g…®n izim, a bar fom…®ra iti, ez…® nan amebam g…®n na bate. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an gavgavim bar nan gavgavim gafira.‚Äô  
\v 31 K…® uab…® a g…®fozir puvat…®, a tina. K…® gumazir kam aghuright…®ma, Israel…®n gumazamiziba a g…®foghasa, kamagh…®n k…® iza d…®pam…®n gumazamiziba rue.‚Äù  
\v 32 Ez…® Jon ua kamagh…®n an gun m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® garima God…®n Duam kuarazir bunbam…®n m…®n God…®n Nguibam ategha m…®ghegha izaghira gumazir kam gis…®n iti.  
\v 33 K…® uab…® a g…®fozir puvat…®. God d…®pam…®n gumazamiziba ruasa na amadaz…® k…® ize. A faragha kamagh…®n na m…®keme, ‚ÄòN…® gant…®ma, God…®n Duam izighr…®gh…®va, gumazitam gis…®n ikiam, a gumazir kamra, a God…®n Duam…®n gumazamiziba ruam.‚Äô  
\v 34 K…® uab…® bizir kam…®n ganigha egha an gun kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, gumazir kamra, a God…®n Otarim.‚Äù 
\s1 4 plan gumaziba Iesus…®n suren gumazibar otifi 
\p  
\v 35 Egha am…®m…®zarakan Jon uan suren gumazir mamning ko ua danganir kam…®n tuivighav iti.  
\v 36 Ez…® a garima Iesus a gitav…®raz…®ma, Jon aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua gan! Kar God…®n Sipsip…®n Nguzim!‚Äù  
\v 37 Ez…® suren gumazir kamning a barazima a kamagh…®n akar kam m…®kemez…®ma, aning ghua Iesus…®n g…®n zui.  
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus ik…®gha gara aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúGua tizim buri?‚Äù Ez…® aning an azara, ‚ÄúRabi, n…® d…®penir manam…®n iti?‚Äù (Ziar kam ‚ÄúRabi‚Äù an m…®ngarim kamak…®n, ‚ÄúTisa.‚Äù)  
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua iz…® ganigh.‚Äù Ez…® aning ghua d…®penir a itim…®n gari. Dughiam, 4 klogh…®n guarat…®zim. Ez…® dughiar kam aning a ko iti. 
\p  
\v 40 Egha Andru, a Iesus…®n g…®n zuir gumazir kamning…®n mav. A Saimon Pitan aveghbuam.  
\v 41 Egha Andru Iesus ategha magh…®ra ghua uan aveghbuam Saimon batogha, egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Mesaian gani.‚Äù (Ziar kam ‚ÄúMesaia‚Äù a kamak…®n, ‚ÄúGumazir God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezim.‚Äù)  
\v 42 Egha Andru Saimon inigha Iesus bagha ghu. Ez…® Iesus an gara egha m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Saimon, Jon…®n Otarim. Eght…® me g…®n ziam ‚ÄòSifas‚Äô n…® dar…®gh n…® d…®ponam.‚Äù (Ziar kam ‚ÄúSifas,‚Äù a ziar kam ‚ÄúPitan‚Äù m…®rara ghu. An m…®ngarim kamak…®n, ‚ÄúDag…®am.‚Äù)\f + \ft (1:42) Ziar kam Sifas, an Aram…®n akam ize. Dughiar kam…®n a Judabar akam. Ez…® ziar kam Pita, a Grigh…®n akam…®n ize.\f* 
\s1 Iesus Filip ko Nataniel…®n dia 
\p  
\v 43 Egha am…®m…®zarakan, Iesus Galilin Distrigh…®n mangasa. Egha a ghua Filip batogha, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan g…®n iz…®!‚Äù  
\v 44 (Filip a Betsaidan nguibam…®n gumazir mam. Andru ko Pitan nguibam, Betsaida.)  
\v 45 Ez…® Filip ghua Nataniel batogha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE gumazir kam…®n ganigha g…®fa, Moses fom…®ra Judabar Arazibar Ak…®nafarim…®n osira gumazir kam…®n gun osiri. Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba uaghan gumazir kam…®n gun osiri. A Nasaret…®n nguibam…®n gumazim Iesus, a Josep…®n otarim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 46 Ez…® Nataniel kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúTi akurvazir bizir aghuitam Nasaret…®n nguibam…®n otivam? Ti puvat…®gham!‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Filip a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…® ganigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 47 Ez…® Iesus garima Nataniel a bagha izi. Ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ganigh. Gumazir izir kam, a guizbang…®ra Israel…®n gumazim. Ez…® ifavarir akatam ko ifavarir arazir tam an itir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 48 Ez…® Nataniel kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh…®n na g…®fo?‚Äù Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúFilip t…®ghar n…®n d…®mamin dughiam…®n, n…® temer figh…®n povim…®n itima, k…® n…®n gani.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 49 Ez…® Nataniel akar kam baregha egha kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúTisa, n…® God…®n Otarim! N…® Israelbar Atrivim!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 50 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n n…® m…®gei, n…® temer figh…®n povim…®n itima, k…® n…®n gani. Ez…® bizir muziarir kam…®n, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan iti. N…® g…®n bizir ekiabar gant…® da bizir kam bar a gafiragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 51 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia g…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n gant…® a kuighr…®gham, eght…® ia God…®n enselbar gant…® da Gumazibar Otarim bagh ghuavanang…®va, ua izighram.‚Äù 
\c 2  
\ms1 Iesus uan gavgavir bar ekiam akakagha mirakel…®n arazibagh ami 
\mr (Sapta 2-4) 
\s1 Iesus d…®pam g…®raz…®ma a wain…®n d…®pam…®n oto 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar pumuning g…®vaz…®ma, gumazir mam Kanan nguibam…®n ikia amizim…®n ikiasa, ez…® amuim…®n ikiamin isam oto. Kanan nguibam a Galilin Distrigh…®n aven iti. Dughiar kam Iesus…®n amebam uaghan iti.\f + \ft (2:1) Iesus amizir mirakel…®n av…®ribar akaba, da Jon…®n ak…®nafarim…®n aven iti. Arazir kabar, an akagha ghaze, a guizbang…®ra Godra. N…® gans…®, Luk 2:11, 2:18-19, Luk 2:23, 3:2, 4:54, 6:2, 6:14, 6:26, 9:16, 11:45, 12:18, ko 12:37.\f* 
\v 2 Ez…® me uaghan Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko men diaz…®ma me uaghan amuim…®n ikiamin isar kam…®n ghuegha iti.  
\v 3 Ez…® wain…®n d…®pam g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus…®n amebam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe ua wain…®n d…®paba puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmebam, kar n…®n bizim, a nan bizim puvat…®. Nan dughiam a t…®ghar…®.‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® an amebam ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúA bizitam damus…® ia m…®k…®mt…®, ia a damu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® d…®penir kam…®n 6 plan dag…®ar m…®ner ekiaba iti, da ekevegha egha vaghvagha 100 litan d…®paba dar iti. Judaba uan rurir arazibar g…®n ghua d…®par kabagh rue.  
\v 7 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa m…®ner kabar d…®paba tuigh.‚Äù Ez…® me da tuiz…®ma da bar izevegha akabagh imara.  
\v 8 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®ner nguzim inigh d…®patam tuigh…®va a inigh…®va gumazir isam…®n faragha zuim bagh mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® ingangarir gumaziba maba inigha zui.  
\v 9 Ez…® d…®par kam wain…®n d…®pam…®n otogha g…®fa, ez…® gumazir isam…®n faragha zuim anepava a barasi, egha a fozir puvat…®, me managh wain…®n d…®par kam ini. Ez…® ingangarir gumazir d…®pam tuiziba, merara fo. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, isam…®n faragha zuir gumazim a gumazir amuim…®n ikiasava amim, an dia,  
\v 10 egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumaziba bar wain…®n d…®par aghuim faragha me gan…®di. Ez…® gumaziba wain…®n av…®rim amegha g…®vaz…®ma, me g…®n wain…®n d…®par mong afangizim an…®di. Ez…® no, n…® wain…®n d…®par aghuim…®n anogoregha, egha dat…®r…®gh…®ra n…® a inigha izi!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Kar mirakel…®n arazir faragha zuir Iesus amizim. A Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam Kanan, mirakel…®n arazir kam gami. Ez…® mirakel…®n kam…®n, Iesus bar uan gavgavir ekiam aka. Ez…® an suren gumaziba an ganigha egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® bizir kabar g…®n, Iesus uan amebam ko aveghbuaba ko an suren gumaziba, me Kanan ategha Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n ghuaghiri. Egha me dughiar mabar nguibar kam…®n iti. 
\s1 Iesus God…®n D…®penim…®n aven dag…®aba bagha ingarir gumaziba batosi 
\r (Matyu 21:12-13 ko Mak 11:15-16 ko Luk 19:45-46) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Israel bagh Itazir Dughiam…®n Isam otivasa rogh…®ra izima, ez…® bizir kam bagha Iesus Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.  
\v 14 Egha a God…®n D…®penim…®n av…®zim…®n aven ghua bizibar garima, gumaziba dag…®aba iniasa bulmakauba ko sipsipba ko kuaraziba amadi. Ez…® a garima dag…®aba uari ikarvazir gumaziba apiaghav iti.  
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus beniba inigha b…®zim…®n m…®n a da ike. Egha a gumaziba ko men sipsipba ko bulmakauba bar me batoke, ez…® me God…®n D…®penim…®n av…®zim ategha zui. Ez…® a dag…®aba uari ikarvazir gumazibar dakoziba akuri da ira dag…®aba ak…®ziragha tintinibar zui.  
\v 16 Ez…® a kamagh…®n gumazir dag…®aba bagha kuaraziba amadiba pamten me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa kuaraziba inigh mang…®! Ia nan Afeziam…®n d…®penim biziba amadir danganim…®n m…®n a damuan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 17 Ez…® an suren gumaziba an amizir arazir kam…®n ganigha, egha me God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akar mam gin…®r…®. Akar kam a kamak…®n, ‚ÄúNan navir averiam bar n…®n d…®penim g…®fuegha egha a baghav…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Judan gumazir aruaba Iesus amizir arazir kam…®n ganigha, egha me kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® mirakel…®n arazir manam damigh en akagh suam, n…® gavgavim ikia gat…®r…®gh…®n arazir kam gami?‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúIa God…®n d…®penir kam ap…®right…®, eght…® k…® dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n uam an ingaright…®ma a tugham.‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe 46 plan azenibar God…®n D…®penir kam…®n ingari. Eght…® n…® ti dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n a ingaright…® a tugham, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus m…®geir God…®n d…®penir kam, an m…®karzimra.  
\v 22 Ez…® God g…®n mozim…®n a gamiz…®ma a ua d…®kafi, ez…® an suren gumaziba ua akar a fom…®ra m…®kemezir kam gin…®r…®. Egha akar God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itim ko akar Iesus m…®kemezir kam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar iti. 
\s1 Iesus gumazibar araziba bar dagh fo 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus Israel bagh Itazir Dughiam…®n Isam…®n Jerusalem…®n itima, gumazamizir av…®rim mirakel…®n arazarazir Iesus amizibar gani. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti.  
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus, a bar men araziba ko n…®ghn…®zibagh fo. Kamagh…®n, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim men itir puvat…®.  
\v 25 A uab…® gumazibar navir averiabar aven itir n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha g…®fa. A fofozitam…®n otevezir puvat…®, eght…® gumazitam gumazibar arazibar gun a m…®k…®man kogham. 
\c 3  
\s1 Iesus Nikodemus ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 Gumazir mam iti, an ziam Nikodemus, a Farisin mam, egha a Judabar gumazir aruar mam.  
\v 2 D…®magarir mam gumazir kam Iesus bagha izegha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e fo, God tisan m…®n n…® amadaz…®ma n…® ize. E fo, God gumazitam ko ikian koght…®ma, eght…® gumazir kam mirakel…®n n…® amir kaba, a tam damuva avegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® bar guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei. Gumazitam ua gumazir igiam…®n otoghan kogh…®va, a God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikian kogham.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® Nikodemus an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®ra gumazim ghurigha g…®vagha egha ua igiam gava? A ti uamategh uan amebam…®n navir averiam…®n mang…®t…® an amebam uam a bategham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, gumazitam d…®pam ko God…®n Duam…®n ua gumazir igiam…®n otoghan kogh, egh a God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikian kogham.  
\v 6 Nguazir kam…®n itir amiziba boriba batima, borir igiaba otifi. Ez…® God…®n Duam gumazim…®n duam gamima, a gumazir igiam…®n oto.  
\v 7 N…® akar k…® n…® m…®kemezim…®n n…® d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®, ‚ÄòIa ua igiabar otifigh.‚Äô  
\v 8 Am…®nim a uan ifongiam…®n g…®n t…®gha egha pura tintinibar vua zui. N…® an n…®g…®nim barasi, egha n…® fozir puvat…®, a managh iza egha ua managh zui. Kamagh…®ra, God…®n Duam gumaziba bar me gamima me igiabar otifi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Nikodemus kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúBizir n…® m…®geir kam, a manmagh…®n otogham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? N…® Israelbar tong…®n itir tisan ekiam, egha n…® ti bizir kabagh fozir puvat…®, o?  
\v 11 K…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, e fozir bizim e a m…®gei. Egha e bizir e ganizim…®n gun m…®gei. Ez…® ia, e m…®kemezir akam ak…®rim ragha a gasara.  
\v 12 K…® nguazir kam…®n bizibar ia m…®keme, ez…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar itir puvat…®. Eght…® kamagh…®n k…® God…®n Nguibam…®n bizibar ia m…®k…®mt…®, ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar ikiam?  
\v 13 Gumazir igharazitam God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabozir pu. Puvat…®. Gumazibar Otarim uab…®ra God…®n Nguibam ategha zaghir…®. 
\p  
\v 14 ‚ÄúFom…®ra Moses gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia kuruzim…®n nedazir aghorim…®n itim a ghufe, eght…® kamagh…®ra me Gumazibar Otarim ghufam.  
\v 15 God kamagh sua, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Gumazibar Otarim…®n itiba, me bar zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. Bizir kam bagh me Gumazibar Otarim ghufam. 
\p  
\v 16 ‚ÄúGod Otarir bar vam…®ra iti. Egha God nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba, bar me gifonge. A kamagh sua, gumazamiziba bar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an Otarim…®n ik…®va ovengan kogh…®va, zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. Bizir kam bagha an Otarir bar vam…®ran kam me gan…®ngi.  
\v 17 God uan Otarim nguazim…®n gumazamizibar jas…®n m…®n me tuis…®ghasa anemadazir puvat…®. A men akurvaghasa anemada.  
\v 18 Gumazim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Otarim…®n ti, a kotiaba puvat…®. Ez…® gumazim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikian aghua, a kot…®n ikia bar ovegha g…®fa. A n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n Otarir vam…®ran kam…®n itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n an ovegha g…®fa.  
\v 19 Ez…® God…®n kotiam…®n m…®ngarim…®n arazim kamak…®n, God…®n angazangarim nguazim…®n izegha g…®fa. Ez…® gumazamiziba, me amir araziba bar ikufi, kamagh…®n amiz…® me m…®tatem bagha bar ifonge, me angazangarim…®n aghua.  
\v 20 Gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba bar, angazangarim…®n apaniba. Men arazir kuraba azenim giran me aghua, kamagh…®n amiz…® me angazangarim…®n izir puvat…®.  
\v 21 Ez…® gumazir guizbang…®n arazim gamim, a God…®n angazangarim…®n izi. A kamagh…®n ifonge, God…®n angazangarim derav…®ra kamagh…®n gumazamizir igharazibar akagham, a God…®n gavgavim…®n uan ingangarim gami. Ez…® kamagh…®n gumazir kam God…®n angazangarim…®n aven izi.‚Äù 
\s1 Jon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, deraghav…®ra bighat…®gha ghaze, Iesus a tina 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® bizir kabar g…®n Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko me Judian Distrigh…®n zui. A me ko danganir kam ikia gumazamiziba rue.  
\v 23 Jon Ainon…®n nguibam…®n ikia gumazamiziba rue, Salim…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®ra. D…®par av…®rim danganir kam…®n ti, ez…® gumazamizir av…®rim rurim iniasa izi.  
\v 24 (Dughiar kam Herot Jon t…®ghar a is…® kalabus dar…®gham.) 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® akavdorozir mam Jon…®n suren gumaziba ko Judan gumazir mam…®n tong…®n oto. Me uari adogha ghaze, e rurir arazir manam…®n g…®n mang…®, God…®n damazim zuegham?  
\v 26 Egha suren gumaziba Jon bagha ghuegha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, gumazir kam fom…®ra n…® ko Jordan…®n d…®pam…®n vong…®n ike, ez…® n…® an gun m…®keme, gumazir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamiziba ruema, gumazamiziba bar a bagha zui.‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® Jon kamagh…®n ikara, ‚ÄúGod…®n uan Nguibam…®n itim, bizitam gumazim danigan koght…®, an a inighan kogham.  
\v 28 K…® fom…®ra akar kam ia m…®keme, ez…® ia uari a baraki, ‚ÄòK…® God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim puvat…®. God na amadaz…®ma k…® an faragha ize.‚Äô  
\v 29 Gumazitam amizitam…®n ikiam, eght…® amizir kam a gumazir kam…®n amuim. Ez…® gumazir kam…®n namakam, a tugha gumazir amuim…®n itim…®n akam baraghasa bar akonge. Ez…® kamagh…®ra agorogem nan navir averiam bar a giz…®fa.  
\v 30 An ziam bar ekevegh mamagh…®ra ik…®t…®, eght…® nan ziam bar mag…®r…®gh. 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúGumazir God…®n Nguibam…®n p…®n ikegha izezim, a bar bizibagh is…®n iti. Ez…® nguazir kam…®n gumazim, a nguazir kam…®n bizibagh amua egha nguazir kam…®n bizibav gei. Ez…® gumazir God…®n Nguibam…®n izezim a bar bizibar is…®n iti.  
\v 32 A bizir a ganiziba ko oraghizibar gun m…®gei. Ez…® gumazitam a m…®kemezir akar katam inigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®.  
\v 33 Ez…® gumazim an akam inigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia, egha tuavir kam…®n kamagh…®n men aka, God a guiz…®n akam m…®gei.  
\v 34 Gumazir God amadazir kam, God uan Duam isa bar a gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a God…®n akam akuri.  
\v 35 Afeziam uan Otarim bar a gifonge, egha biziba bar an agharim gat…®z…® a bar dagh atifa.  
\v 36 Gumazim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Otarim…®n ti, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iti. Ez…® gumazim Otarim…®n akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim inian kogham, God…®n an…®ngagharim an ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 4  
\s1 Iesus Samarian amizim ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Farisiba kamagh…®n oraki, Iesus gumazamizir av…®riba rue ez…® gumazamizir kaba an suren gumazibar otifi. Ez…® men d…®bobonim Jon…®n suren gumazibar d…®bobonim gafira.  
\v 2 (Guizbang…®ra, Iesus uab…® gumazamiziba ruer puvat…®. An suren gumaziba me rue.)  
\v 3 Iesus kamagh…®n fo, Farisiba orazima gumazir av…®riba an suren gumazamizibar otifi, kamagh…®n a Judian Distrigh ategha uamategha Galilin Distrigh…®n ghu.  
\v 4 Ez…® tuavir a zuir kam, a Samarian Distrigh abigha ghu. 
\p  
\v 5 Egha a ghua Samarian Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibar mam…®n oto, an ziam Sikar. Ez…® Sikar…®n nguibam, a nguazir Jekop uan otarim Josep gan…®ngizim…®n borogh…®ra iti.  
\v 6 Jekop fom…®ra kuizir mozir d…®pam iti, a nguibar kam…®n ti. Ez…® Iesus iza ghua bar am…®ra. Egha a mozir d…®par kam…®n borogh…®n apera. Ez…® dughiam an aruer ar…®zim…®n ghu. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Samarian amizir mam, a d…®pam tuasa izi, ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®patam na dan…®ngam, o?‚Äù  
\v 8 (Dughiar kam…®n Iesus…®n suren gumaziba daghebagh ivezasa nguibam…®n ghu.) 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Samarian amizim a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Judan gumazim ez…® k…® Samarian amizim. Manmagh sua, n…® d…®pam ramasa na m…®gei?‚Äù (Amizir kam fo, Judaba me Samarian gumazamiziba ko itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n an akar kam Iesus m…®gei.)  
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n amizim ikara, ‚ÄúN…®, God gumazamizibagh an…®ngizir bizir aghuim g…®fogh…®va, egh gumazir d…®pam bagha n…® m…®geir kam g…®fogh…®va, egh n…® an azaraght…®, a d…®par ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim n…® danigam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® amizim a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, n…® m…®neba pu. Mozir d…®par kam bar kone. Eght…® d…®par ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim, n…® managh a inigham?  
\v 12 En ovavim Jekop mozir d…®par kam e gan…®ngi. Egha a uab…® uan boriba ko bulmakauba ko an as…®ziba, me bar mozir d…®par kam ame. Ez…® n…® ghaze, n…® ti Jekop gafira, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumaziba bar d…®par kam ramegh, men kuariba ua p…®ram.  
\v 14 Ez…® gumazitam k…® dan…®ngamin d…®par kam ramegham, an kuarim dughiatam…®n uam an p…®ran kogham. Puvat…®. D…®par k…® dan…®ngamin kam, a d…®par nguazim…®n averiam…®n ikiava otivi mogh…®ra, an navir averiam…®n otivam. Egh d…®par ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dir kam otiv mamagh…®ra ik…®va, egh zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim a dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, d…®par kam na dan…®ng. Eght…® nan kuarim g…®n ua p…®ran kogham, eght…® k…® ua kagh iz…® d…®pam tuan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® uan pam…®n diagh…®va egh gua kagh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® amizim a ikara, ‚ÄúK…® paba puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAre, n…® deragha m…®gei, n…® paba puvat…®.  
\v 18 Guizbang…®ra, n…® faragha 5 pla paba iti. Ez…® gumazir n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itim, a guizbang…®ra n…®n pam puvat…®. N…®n akar kam a bar guizbang…®ra.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® amizim a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, n…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam.  
\v 20 En ovaviba me m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n uari akuva, egha God…®n ziam fe. Ez…® ia Judaba ghaze, danganir gumaziba mang…®va God…®n ziam fam, a Jerusalem…®n iti.‚Äù\f + \ft (4:20) M…®ghs…®ar amizir kam an gun m…®geim, a Gerazim…®n M…®ghs…®am, a Samarian Distrigh…®n iti. Samarian gumazamiziba m…®ghs…®ar kamra ghuava God…®n ziam fe. N…® deragh foghs…®, Luk 9:53…®n vez…®n itir akam…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmizim, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ik…®. Dughiatam otoght…®ma ia m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n Afeziam…®n ziam fan kogh…®va, egh uaghan Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n an ziam fan kogham.  
\v 22 Ia Samariaba ia fozir puvat…®zir God, ia an ziam fe. Ez…® e Judaba e fozir God, e an ziam fe. E fo, God…®n gumazamizibar akurvazir ingangarim, a faragh Judabar agharim…®n ikegh egh g…®n gumazamizir igharaziba bagh mangam.  
\v 23 Ez…® dughiar otivamim, an otogha g…®fa, ez…® gumazamiziba bar guizbang…®ra Afeziam…®n ziam fasa, me an Duam…®n gavgavim ko guizbang…®n arazim…®n an ziam fam. Ez…® Afeziam, gumazamizir kamagh…®n amiba, me an ziam fasa a bar ifonge.  
\v 24 God, a Duam. Ez…® gumazir an ziam feba, me God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim ko guizbang…®n arazim…®n an ziam fe.‚Äù\f + \ft (4:23-24) Gumazir maba akar kam ‚ÄúGod…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n,‚Äù me a giragha ghaze, ‚Äúme uari uan duabar gavgavim…®n.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fo, Mesaia a izam (a God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.) A izamin dughiam, a biziba bar e m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar k…®rara, dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® ko m…®gei.‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®geima, dughiar kam…®n an suren gumaziba uamategha izi. Me an garima an amizir mam ko uaning m…®geima, ez…® me okam n…®ghn…®si. Egha tav kamagh…®n amizim…®n azarazir puvat…®, ‚ÄúN…® tizim iniasa?‚Äù Egha tav Iesus…®n azarazir puvat…®, ‚ÄúN…® tizim sua amizir kam ko m…®gei?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® amizir kam uan m…®nem ataki, egha uamategha nguibam…®n ghu. Egha kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei,  
\v 29 ‚ÄúIa iz…® gumazir mam…®n ganigh. K…® fom…®ra amizir araziba, a bar dar na m…®keme. Ka ti gumazir kamra, God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim?‚Äù  
\v 30 Egha me nguibam ategha, Iesus bagha izi. 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Iesus…®n suren gumaziba agakaghora kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, n…® dam…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúDagher k…® damamim, ia a g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 33 Ez…® an suren gumaziba uarira kamagh…®n uariv gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam ti a bagha dagheba inigha iza a gan…®ngi?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan daghemra kara, k…® God…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n zui, a gumazir na amadaz…® k…® izezim. Ez…® k…® a na gan…®ngizir ingangarim, a g…®vagham.  
\v 35 Ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚Äò4 plan iakiniba g…®vaght…®, e dar g…®n azenibar aghoram.‚Äô Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, ia tintinibar gan…®va egh derav…®ra azenibar gan. Dagheba aghuigha g…®fa, ez…® azenibar aghoramin dughiam otogha g…®fa!  
\v 36 Gumazir dagheba isim, a dat…®r…®gh…®n uan ivezim isi, egha zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim bagha dagheba akufi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, gumazir dagheba oparim ko gumazir dagheba isim aning v…®rara bar akuegham.  
\v 37 Akar kam a guizbang…®ra, ‚ÄòGumazir mam azenim opari, ez…® gumazir igharazim an dagheba isi.‚Äô  
\v 38 K…®, ia faragha ingarizir puvat…®zir azenim…®n dagheba iniasa, k…® ia amada. Gumazir igharaziba azenir kam…®n ingari, ez…® ia ghua me uan gavgavim…®n oparizir otivizir dagheba isi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Amizir kam faragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam, k…® fom…®ra amizir araziba, a bar dar na m…®keme.‚Äù Ez…® nguibar kam…®n itir Samarian gumazamizir av…®riba, me an akam baregha egha kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n iti.  
\v 40 Egha Samariaba a bagha ize, egha me uarir gan ikiasa agakaghorav…®ra iti. Ez…® a dughiar pumuning…®n me ko iti.  
\v 41 Ez…® gumazamizir igharazir av…®rir maba, me uaghan Iesus…®n akam baregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. 
\p  
\v 42 Egha me kamagh…®n amizim m…®gei, ‚ÄúE n…®n akamra baregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gumazir kam…®n itir pu. Puvat…®. E uari an akam baraki, egha e fo, gumazir kamra, a guizbang…®ra nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizibar Akurvazir Gumazim. Kamagh…®n e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n borim gamiz…®ma, a ua dera 
\p  
\v 43 Ez…® Iesus dughiar pumuning…®n Samarian adarazi ko ikegha g…®vagha, egha nguibar kam ategha Galilin Distrigh…®n ghu.  
\v 44 Iesus uab…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gami, ‚ÄúGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, a uan nguibamra ziaba puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 45 Galilin Distrigh…®n itir gumazamiziba, me uaghan Israel bagh Itazir Dughiam…®n Isam bagha Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n ghue, ez…® Iesus dughiar kam…®n mirakel…®n av…®ribagh amiz…®ma me dar gani. Ez…® kamagh…®n Iesus dat…®r…®gh…®n uamategha ghua Galilin otoz…®ma, ez…® Galilin gumazamiziba bar akuegha a ini. 
\p  
\v 46 Ez…® Iesus ua Kanan nguibam…®n ghu, a Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam. A faragha nguibar kam…®n d…®pam giraz…®ma a wain…®n d…®pam…®n oto. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir mam, a Kanan nguibam…®n iti. Ez…® an otarim ar…®a, Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n iti.  
\v 47 Ez…® gumazir kam akam kamagh…®n a baraki, Iesus Judian Distrigh ategha Galilin Distrigh…®n ize. Ez…®ma a Iesus bagha ghua agakaghora ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n mag…®r…®, egh nan otarim damight…®, a ua deraka. Nan otarim bar ovengasava ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 48 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mirakelba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibar ganan kogh…®va, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikian kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 49 Ez…® ingangarir gumazir kam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, n…® zuam…®ra izighir…®. puvat…®ght…®ma, nan otarim aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 50 Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®, n…®n otarim angamra ikiam.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n akam…®n ikiava, egha a ghu. 
\p  
\v 51 Egha gumazir kam tuavim…®n ghuav…®ra itima, an ingangarir gumaziba iza tuavim…®n a bato, egha me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n otarim an angamra iti!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 52 Ez…® a men azara, dughiar manamra borim mong dera. Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúBogh…®naron 1 klogh…®n aruer ar…®zim…®n, an ar…®mariam g…®vaz…® m…®karzim orangi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 53 Ez…® afeziam fo, bogh…®naron dughiar kamra Iesus a m…®keme, ‚ÄúN…®n otarim an angamra ikiam.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itima, an adarazi uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti.  
\v 54 Kar dughiar namba 2, Iesus Judian Distrigh ategha ua iza Galilin Distrigh…®n ikiava mirakel…®n mam uam a gami. 
\c 5  
\ms1 Iesus uan ingangarim gamua egha Sabat…®n dughiabar gumazamizibar sure gami 
\mr (Sapta 5-10) 
\s1 Iesus Betesdan mozir d…®pam…®n gumazir mam gamiz…® a ua dera 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®, Judabar isar ekiam otoz…®ma, ez…® Iesus isam bagha Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.\f + \ft (5:1) Jon…®n ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir saptan 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, ko 10, Iesus Sabat…®n dughiaba ko Judabar Isar Ekiam…®n dughiabar, ingangarir av…®ribar akaba iti. N…® gans…®, Luk 5:1, 5:9, 6:4, 7:2, 10:22. Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Jon kamagh…®n en akaghasa, Iesus a Judabar Dughiar Ekiaba, a uab…® dar m…®ngarim. N…® gans…®, Luk 2:13 ko 2:23 ko 11:55.\f* 
\v 2 Ez…® Jerusalem…®n mozir d…®par ekiar mam iti, ez…® Hibrun akam me Betesda, a gar…®si. A Sipsipba Aven Zuir Tiar Akar Ekiam…®n borogh…®ra iti. Ez…® mozir d…®par kam…®n m…®riam azuarir 5 pla iti.\f + \ft (5:2) Dughiar kam Jerusalem nguibam…®n d…®vazir bar ekiam iti. Ez…® tiar akar av…®riba an iti. Ez…® tiar akar kabar mam, an ziam Sipsipba Aven Zuir Tiar Akam. Betesdan mozir d…®par ekiam, a tiar akar kam borogh…®ra iti.\f* 
\v 3-4 Ez…® azuarir kaba ar…®mariar gumazamizir av…®rim dar iti, damazir okav…®r…®ziba ko suer kuraba, ko soroghafariba am…®raziba.\f + \ft (5:3-4) Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, akar igharazir mam uaghan vez…®n kam iti. Akar kam kamak…®n: ‚ÄúMe d…®par kam siravamangasa, me a m…®zuai. Dughiar maba Ekiam…®n ensel…®n mam ghuaghirigha d…®pam gamima a siravamadi. D…®pam siravamangigha g…®vaz…®, gumazir ar…®mariar manam itim, a d…®pam…®n aven mag…®r…®gh, egh a ua deragham.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 5 Gumazir mam an azuarir mam…®n iti, an suemning bar am…®raz…®ma a 38 plan azenibar ar…®mariar kam an iti.  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus gumazir kam…®n garima a ir…®ghav iti, ez…® a fo, a fom…®ram ar…®a iti. Ez…® Iesus an azara, ‚ÄúN…® ua deraghasa n…® ifonge?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® ar…®mariar gumazim kamagh…®n Iesus…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, k…® akurvazir gumaziba puvat…®. D…®pam s…®rvamadir dughiam, gumazitam na inigha ghua mozir d…®pam…®n averiam gat…®zir puvat…®. K…® uab…® mangasa ifonge, ez…® gumazir igharaziba faragha ghuaghira egha na gafisi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh…®va uan daguivsiaba inigh, daru mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 9 Ez…® gumazir kam…®n suemning zuam…®ra ua dera. Ez…® a uan daguivsiaba inigha egha zui. 
\p Ez…® dughiar kam a Sabat…®n dughiam,  
\v 10 ez…® Judaba me gumazir kam…®n ganigha egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n Sabat…®n dughiam. Moses Osirizir Araziba, da ghaze, n…® Sabat…®n dughiam…®n uan daguivsiaba ater daruan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 11 Ez…® a kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir na gamiz…®ma k…® derazim, a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® d…®kavigh…®va uan daguivsiaba inigh, daru mang…®.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúGumazir manamra, n…® m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® d…®kavigh…®va uan daguivsiaba inigh, daru mang…®.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® gumazir ua derazir kam a fozir puvat…®, tinara a m…®keme. Dughiar kam gumazamizir av…®rim nguibar kam…®n iti, ez…® Iesus men tong…®n suiaghr…®gha ghu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, gumazir kam fozir puvat…®, tina an akura. 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® g…®n Iesus God…®n d…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n aven ghua an garima a iti. Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ua dera. N…® uam arazir kuratam damuan mark…®. N…® oraghan koght…®, os…®mt…®zir bar ekiatam n…® batogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® gumazir kam ghua kamagh…®n Judabav gei, ‚ÄúGumazir na gamiz…® k…® derazim, a Iesusra.‚Äù  
\v 16 Iesus Sabat…®n dughiam…®n bizir kabagh ami, bizir kam…®n Judaba os…®mt…®ziba Iesus gar…®gha ghaze, an en apanim. 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúNan Afeziam a zurara ingara iza dat…®r…®k…®n. Ez…® k…® uaghan k…® ingari.‚Äù  
\v 18 Ez…® Judaba me akar kam baregha me fo, Iesus Sabat…®n dughiam…®n Arazim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®, egha a uaghan ghaze, God guizbang…®ra nan Afeziamra. Akar kam…®n, a uab…® uab…® gamigha egha God…®n m…®n oto. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Judaba Iesus m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa me bar ifonge. 
\s1 God…®n Otarim a ingangarim damuamin gavgavim iti 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus Judabar akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, Otarim bizitam a uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n a damighan kogham. Puvat…®. An Afeziam…®n gari, an amir biziba darara a dagh ami. Egha bizir Afeziam amiba, Otarim uaghan dagh ami.  
\v 20 Afeziam bar Otarim gifonge, egha bizir a uab…® amiba, a bar ada isa uan Otarim…®n aka. Afeziam kamagh sua, a ia damut…® ia d…®gavir kuram damuam, kamagh…®n a ingangarir ekiar igharaziba sara uaghan uan Otarim…®n akagham, da ingangarir an amigha g…®vazibagh afiragham.  
\v 21 Afeziam gumazir ariaghrezibagh amima me ua d…®kavima an angamra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim me gan…®di. Ez…® kamagh…®ra Otarim uaghan gumazir a m…®seveziba angamra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim me gan…®di.  
\v 22 Afeziam kot…®n gumazitam…®n araziba tuis…®zir puvat…®. Egha gumazibar araziba tuis…®ghamin ingangarim, an a isa Otarim gan…®ngi.  
\v 23 Afeziam kamagh sua, gumaziba bar Afeziam…®n ziam fe mogh…®n, me Otarim…®n ziam fam, kamagh…®n a gumaziba tuis…®ghamin ingangarim isa Otarim gan…®ngi. Gumazim Otarim…®n ziam fer puvat…®, an Afeziar Otarim amadazim…®n ziam fer puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazim nan akam baragha, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Afeziar na amadazim…®n ikiava, egha a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iti. A kotiaba puvat…®. An ovevem ategha, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n an angamra iti. 
\p  
\v 25 ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, dughiar otivamim, a dat…®r…®gh…®n otogha g…®fa. Ez…® gumazir ariaghreziba me God…®n Otarim…®n akam baragham. Gumazamizir a baraghiziba, me angamra ikiam.  
\v 26 Afeziam, a uab…® ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®ngamin gavgavim iti. Kamagh…®ra a uan Otarim gamiz…®, a uaghan ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®ngamin gavgavim iti.  
\v 27 A Gumazibar Otarim, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Afeziam gumazibar araziba tuis…®ghamin gavgavim a gan…®ngi.  
\v 28 Ia nan akar kam inigh egh d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. Dughiam otivasava amima gumazir ariaghreziba, me bar Otarim…®n akam baragham.  
\v 29 Egh me bar moziba ategh azenim…®n izam. Gumazamizir arazir aghuibagh amiziba, me ua d…®kavigh…®va egh zurara angamra ikiam. Eght…® gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiziba, me ua d…®kavigh…®va kotiam…®n ikiam, eght…® k…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®mam, me bar hel…®n mang…®va ivezir kuram iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Marazi uaghan ghaze, Iesus a tina 
\p  
\v 30 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mang…® bizitam damighan kogham. K…® akar Afeziam da inizim…®n g…®n ghua, egha gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®si. K…® uab…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. K…® Afeziam…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n zui, anemadaz…®ma k…® ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® gumazamizibar araziba derav…®ra da tuis…®si, ez…® nan kotiam a bar guizbang…®ra ghua egha bar dera. 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúEght…® k…® uab…® ua bagh uan ingangariba ko arazibar gun m…®k…®mt…®ma eght…® gumaziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim k…® gun m…®geir akar kam…®n ikian mark…®.\f + \ft (5:31) N…® Lo 19:15…®n gan.\f* 
\v 32 Ez…® igharazitav a iti, egha a uaghan nan araziba ko nan ingangaribar gun m…®gei. Ez…® k…® fo, a kon gun m…®geir akam guizbang…®ra.\f + \ft (5:32) Iesus ‚Äúigharazitav‚Äù m…®g…®a, a uan Afeziam God…®n m…®gei.\f* 
\p  
\v 33 ‚ÄúIarara fom…®ra gumazir maba amangiz…® me Jon bagha ghuez…® a nan gun m…®keme, ez…® an akam guizbang…®ra.  
\v 34 K…® uab…®, k…® gumazitam…®n akam nan akam gavgavim a dan…®ngasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha k…® God ian akurvaghasa, k…® ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Jon…®n akam…®n gun ia m…®gei.  
\v 35 Jon a lam…®n m…®n ikia isia angazangarim gumazamizibagh an…®di. Ez…® dughiar otevim…®n ia an akam iniasa ifongez…® ez…® Jon…®n angazangarim ia gisiragha ia gamima ia bar akonge. 
\p  
\v 36 ‚ÄúEz…® nan gun m…®geir akar mam iti, a Jon…®n akam gafira, akar kam dat…®r…®gh…®n a nan gun ia m…®gei. Afeziam, k…® ingangarir kam damuva egh aneg…®vasa, na gan…®ngi. Ez…® ingangarir k…® amir kaba, da bar deraghav…®ra nan gun gumazamizibav m…®gei, Afeziam na amadaz…® k…® ize.  
\v 37 Ez…® Afeziar na amadaz…® k…® izezim, a uab…® nan gun m…®gei. Ez…® ia tong an akam barazir puvat…®. Egha ia dughiatam an guam…®n ganizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 38 Ia Afeziam amadazir gumazir kam…®n akam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®. Ian arazir kaba ian gun m…®gei, Afeziam…®n akam uaghan ian navir averiabar itir puvat…®.\f + \ft (5:38) Gumazir Afeziam amadazir kam, a Iesus uab…®.\f* 
\v 39 Ia ghaze, akar God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itim, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim ia gan…®di. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia akar God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itibar gara da tuis…®si. Ez…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim uaghan nan gun m…®gei!  
\v 40 Ez…® ia na bagh iz…® zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim inian aghua. 
\p  
\v 41 ‚ÄúK…® gumaziba da ziar ekiam iniasa, egha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabagh amir puvat…®.  
\v 42 Ez…® k…® ia g…®fo. Ian navir averiabar, ia guizbang…®ra God gifongezir puvat…®.\f + \ft (5:42) Gumazir maba akar kam giragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n apangkuvim ian navibar itir puvat…®.‚Äù\f* 
\v 43 K…® uan Afeziam…®n ziam…®n ize, ez…® ia nan akam baraghan aghua. Eght…® gumazitam uab…® uan ziam…®n izeght…®, ia an akam zuam…®ram a baregham.  
\v 44 Ia uan adarazira me da ziar ekiaba isi. Ez…® God uab…®ra ziar ekiam an…®dima, ia a inian aghua. Egh ia arazir kabar amuva, egh ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikiam? Bar puvat…®gham! 
\p  
\v 45 ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, k…® Afeziam…®n damazim…®n akam ia gasam. Puvat…®. Gumazir akam ia gasamim, a Moses uab…®, a gumazir kam ia ghaze, a ian akuragham.  
\v 46 Ez…® akar Moses osiriziba, da nan gun m…®gei. Kamagh…®n, ia Moses…®n akam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®va, egh uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan akam…®n ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia guizbang…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Moses…®n akam ko nan akam…®n itir puvat…®.  
\v 47 Ez…® kamagh…®n ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Moses osirizir akabar itir puvat…®, egh ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim na akam…®n ikiam?‚Äù 
\c 6  
\s1 Iesus dagheba isa 5,000…®n gumazibagh an…®di 
\r (Matyu 14:13-21 ko Mak 6:30-44 ko Luk 9:10-17) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® bizir kabar g…®n Iesus Galilin D…®pam…®n dadarir vuem…®n ghu, d…®pam…®n ziar mam Taiberias.  
\v 2 Gumazamizir av…®rim faraghav…®ra an garima a mirakel…®n arazarazibar ar…®mariar gumazibagh amima me ua dera. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me dat…®r…®gh…®n an g…®n zui.  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabogha, egha uan suren gumaziba ko aperaghav iti.  
\v 4 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n Isam otivasa rogh…®ra izi.  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus garagharua egha garima gumazamizir av…®rir ekiam a bagha izi. Ez…® a kamagh…®n Filip…®n azara, ‚ÄúE managh gumazamizir kaba bagh daghebagh ivezegh me dan…®ngam?‚Äù  
\v 6 (Ez…® Iesus Filip…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim, gavgavim a dan…®ngasava, akar kam puram a gami. Iesus uab…® bizir a damuamim g…®fo.)  
\v 7 Ez…® Filip a ikara, ‚ÄúE 200 kina inigh bret givezeght…®, da bar gumazamizibar tughat…®ghan kogham, me vaghvagh bret…®n akuar muziariba ini dar amam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumazibar mav, an ziam Andru, a Saimon Pitan aveghbuam, a kamagh…®n m…®gei,  
\v 9 ‚ÄúOtarir mam a kagh iti, a bret…®n me balin daghem…®n ingarizir 5 pla, ko osirir pumuning iti. Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rir ekiam iti. Kamagh…®n bret…®n ko osirir kamning, da manmagh…®n en akuragham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazamizibav m…®k…®mt…®ma me dapiagh.‚Äù (Grazir av…®rim danganir kam…®n iti.) Ez…® gumazamiziba apia. Egha men tong…®n, 5000…®n gumaziba iti.  
\v 11 Me apiaghav itima, ez…® Iesus bret…®n kam inigha God m…®nabagha egha gumazamizibagh an…®di. A uaghan osirir pumuning kamagh…®ra aning gami. A me gan…®di, ez…® me uan ifongiam…®n amegha tughat…®. 
\p  
\v 12 Me amegha naviba bar iz…®vaz…®ma Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa dagher nar ikiav…®ra itiba bar da akumakumigh. Taba pura ikian mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 13 Gumaziba, 5 plan bret…®n me balin daghem ingariziba, me da amegha g…®vaz…®ma bret…®n naba iti. Ez…® suren gumaziba bret…®n nar muziarir itiba akumakumigha egha 12 plan ak…®rabagh aghuiz…® da iz…®fa.  
\v 14 Ez…® gumazamiziba mirakel…®n arazarazir Iesus amizir kam…®n ganigha, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra kar God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, God nguazir kam…®n anemangasa m…®keme!‚Äù  
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus akar kam baregha egha a fo, me iz…®va an suiragh…®va, egh a damight…® a men atrivim…®n ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma a danganir kam ategha egha uab…®ra uamategha m…®ghs…®am…®n ghu. 
\s1 Iesus Galilin D…®pam gis…®n arua zui 
\r (Matyu 14:22-33 ko Mak 6:45-52) 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® guarat…®zir kam…®n Iesus…®n suren gumaziba d…®pam…®n ghuaghiri.  
\v 17 Egha me bot…®n mam inigha egha d…®pam abigha Kaperneam…®n nguibam bagha zui. Iesus t…®ghar me bativam, ez…® am…®nim p…®righa g…®fa.  
\v 18 Ez…® am…®nir dafam oto, egha ongarim givaima an ekiabar d…®kafi  
\v 19 Ez…® me 5 o 6 plan kilomitan ghua pul gamua ghuava, egha me garima Iesus d…®pam gis…®n arua ghuava bot…®n borogh…®ra zui. Ez…® me bar atiatingi.  
\v 20 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei ‚ÄúKar k…®rara izi. Ia atiatingan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…® me a inigh bot…®n aven izasa bar ifonge, ez…® bot zuam…®ra danganim me zuim…®n oto. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba Iesus buri 
\p  
\v 22 Am…®m…®zarakan, gumazamizir d…®pam…®n vong…®n ikiav…®ra ikeziba, me fo, bot…®n vam…®ra bogh…®naron ike, egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko bot…®n kam…®n ghuzir puvat…®. Suren gumazibara bot…®n kam…®n ghue.  
\v 23 Ez…® Taiberias…®n nguibam…®n bot…®n maba, da danganir kam borogh…®ra izi, danganir Ekiam God…®n m…®nabagha egha bret gumazir av…®ribagh an…®ngiz…® me amezim.  
\v 24 Ez…® gumazamiziba me kamagh…®n ganigha fo, Iesus itir puvat…®z…®ma, an suren gumaziba uaghan itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bot…®n kabar ghuavanega, egha Iesus buriasa Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n zui. 
\s1 Iesus, a dagher ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® gumazamiziba d…®pam…®n vong…®n Iesus batogha g…®fa, egha me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, n…® manad…®zogh…®n kagh ize?‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra k…® ia m…®gei, ia mirakel…®n arazarazir ia ganiziba dagh n…®ghn…®gha iza na buri, o? Puvat…®. K…® ghaze, ia dagher k…® ia gan…®ngizir kam amegha egha ian naviba bar izefe, ez…® bizir kam bagha ia na buri.  
\v 27 Ia dagher kuraghriba bagh ingar da inian mark…®. Ia dagher zurara ikia mamagh…®ra itim bagh ingar…®va a inigh, kar dagher zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim an…®dim. Afeziam God kamagh…®n ian aka, Gumazibar Otarim, a uab…®n torogha gavgavim a gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dagher kam, Gumazibar Otarim a ia dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúE manmagh…®n damigh…®va egh e God…®n ingangarim damuam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúGod…®n ingangarim kamak…®n. Ia gumazir God amadazir kam, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúN…® mirakel…®n arazarazir manam damight…® e ganigh…®va egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…®n ikiam? N…® tizim damigham?  
\v 31 En ovaviba dagher mam an ziam mana, me gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia aneme. God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akam m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ‚ÄòA God…®n Nguibam…®n daghem me gan…®ngiz…®ma me aneme.‚Äô‚Äù 
