\v 32 Ez…® Iesus me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ka Moses God…®n Nguibam…®n daghem ia gan…®ngizir pu. Puvat…®. Ka nan Afeziam a guizbang…®n Uan Nguibam…®n daghem ia gan…®ngi.  
\v 33 Dagher God e gan…®ngizir kam, a God…®n Nguibam ategha izaghir…®, a nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamiziba gamima me ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® dagher kam zurara e dan…®ngv…®ra ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uab…®, dagher ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim. Gumazir na bagha izim, a ua m…®tiriam an aghan kogham. Ez…® gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim, a d…®pam ram…®s…® kuarim uam an p…®ran kogham.  
\v 36 K…® ia m…®keme, ia nan ganigha g…®fa, egha ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir puvat…®.  
\v 37 Ez…® gumazamizir Afeziam na gan…®ngiziba, me bar na bagh izam. Egh gumazir na bagh izamim, k…® a batueghan kogham.  
\v 38 K…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mangasa God…®n Nguibam ategha izaghir…®zir puvat…®. K…® Afeziar na amadazim…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n mangasa k…® izaghir…®.  
\v 39 Ez…® Afeziar na amadazim…®n ifongiam, a kamak…®n, k…® gumazamizir a na gan…®ngizitam ateghan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n me damight…® me bar ua d…®kavigham.  
\v 40 Nan Afeziam…®n ifongiam kamak…®n, gumaziba bar Otarim…®n ganigh…®va egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®va, me zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. Eght…® God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam otoght…® k…® me damight…® me ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® Judaba akar kam baraki, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® dagher kam, God…®n Nguibam ategha egha izaghir…®,‚Äù egha me atarava egha uarigh imobi.  
\v 42 Me ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam a Iesus, Josep…®n otarim. E an afeziam ko amebam g…®fo. Ez…® manmagh sua a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® God…®n Nguibam ategha, egha k…® zaghir…®?‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 43 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúIa atara egha uarigh imobir arazir kam atakigh.  
\v 44 Gumazitam uab…® uan ifongiam…®n na bagh izeghan kogham. Puvat…®. Afeziar na amadazim, an n…®ghn…®zim fegh…®va egh a inigh na bagh izam. Eght…® God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam k…® mozim…®n a damight…® a ua d…®kavigh…®va angamra ikiam.  
\v 45 Akar kam kamagh…®n God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar Ak…®nafarim…®n iti, ‚ÄòGod bar gumazamizibar sure damuam.‚Äô Ez…® kamagh…®n gumazamiziba Afeziam…®n akam baregha egha Afeziam da fofozim isa, me na bagha izi. 
\p  
\v 46 ‚ÄúGumazitam Afeziam…®n ganizir puvat…®. Gumazir Afeziam ko ikegha izezir kam, a uab…®ra Afeziam…®n gani.  
\v 47 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iti.  
\v 48 K…® uab…®, k…® dagher ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim.  
\v 49 Ian ovavir kaba me, dagher ziam mana, me gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia aneme, egha ariagh…®re.  
\v 50 Ez…® dagher kam God…®n Nguibam ategha izaghir…®, gumazamiziba anem…®va, egh me aremeghan kogham.  
\v 51 K…® uab…® dagher kam, ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim, God…®n Nguibam ategha egha zaghir…®. Eght…® gumazitam dagher kamra amegh…®va, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. Dagher k…® a dan…®ngamim, a nan nivaf…®zim. K…® kamagh sua, nguazim…®n gumazamiziba me angamra ikiam, kamagh…®n k…® me bagh uan nivaf…®zim anenigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 52 Ez…® Judaba akar kam baregha egha me uari tong…®n uarir atara ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam manmagh…®n uan nivaf…®zim e danight…® e anemam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 53 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra k…® ia m…®gei, ia Gumazibar Otarim…®n nivaf…®zim rameghan kogh…®va, egh an ghuzim rameghan kogh…®va, egh ia angamra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim ian ikian kogham.  
\v 54-55 Nan nivaf…®zim a guiz…®n daghem, ez…® nan ghuzim a guiz…®n apir bizim. Kamagh…®n ami, gumazim nan nivaf…®zim apava egha nan ghuzim api, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iti. Eght…® God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n k…® a damight…® a ua mozim…®n d…®kavigham.  
\v 56 Ez…® gumazim nan nivaf…®zim apava egha nan ghuzim api, a nan poroghav iti, ez…® k…® an poroghav iti.  
\v 57 Afeziar ik…®r…®m…®rir angamra itim an…®dim, a na amadaz…®ma k…® ize, ez…® k…® Afeziam…®n gavgavim…®n angamra iti. Ez…® kamagh…®ra gumazim nan nivaf…®zim api, a nan gavgavim…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir angamra itim iniam.  
\v 58 Dagher kamra, a God…®n Nguibam ategha izaghir…®. Egha dagher kam, a dagher ian ovaviba fom…®ram anemegha g…®n ariaghrezim…®n m…®n garir pu. Puvat…®. Gumazir dagher kam apim, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam.‚Äù  
\v 59 Iesus Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n itir God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ikia, egha a gumazamizibar sure gamua akar kam me gan…®ngi. 
\s1 Iesus…®n akaba, da zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim an…®di 
\p  
\v 60 Ez…® suren gumaziba Iesus…®n akar kam baregha, egha men av…®rim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAkar kam e gamima e n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami. Tina akar kam baragham?‚Äù  
\v 61 Ez…® Iesus uan navir averiam…®n aven kamagh…®n fo, an suren gumaziba puv…®ra akar a m…®kemezim m…®g…®a imobi. Ez…® a men azara, ‚ÄúAkar kam ti ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba gas…®ghas…®si, o?  
\v 62 Egh ia Gumazibar Otarim…®n ganight…®, a nguibar a fom…®ra ikezim…®n ua ghuavanaboght…®, eght…® ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®gham?  
\v 63 God…®n Duam uab…®, angamra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim gumazamizibagh an…®di. Gumazim…®n gavgavim tong ian akuraghan kogham. Akar k…® ia m…®kemezir kaba, da God…®n Duam…®n bizim, da angamra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim ia gan…®di.  
\v 64 Ez…® gumazir ian tong…®n itir maba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba nan itir puvat…®.‚Äù (Iesus fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir puvat…®zir gumazibagh fo. Egha a gumazir a is…® apanibar dafarim dar…®ghamin kam g…®fo.)  
\v 65 Egha Iesus ua me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itir puvat…®, ez…® bizir kam bagha, k…® ia m…®keme, ‚ÄòAfeziam gavgavim gumazitam danigan koght…®, kamagh…®n gumazir kam na bagh izeghan kogham.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 66 Iesus akar kam…®n gun m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, an suren gumazir av…®rim anetegha ua ghue, egha uam a ko aruir puvat…®.  
\v 67 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n 12 plan suren gumazibar azara, ‚ÄúEz…® ia? Ia ti uaghan na ategh mangasa?‚Äù  
\v 68 Ez…® Saimon Pita an akam ikara, ‚ÄúEkiam, e tina bagh mangam? N…®n akabara, da zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim an…®di.  
\v 69 Ez…® e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikiava, egha derav…®ra kamagh…®n fo, n…® gumazir God…®n damazim…®n bar zuegha arazir kuram n…®n puvat…®zim, God ua bagha n…® ginaba.‚Äù  
\v 70 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? K…® uab…® ia 12 plan suren gumaziba m…®sefe. Ez…® ian tong…®n itir mav, a duar kuram.‚Äù  
\v 71 A Judas…®n m…®gei, a Saimon Iskariot…®n otarim, a 12 plan suren gumazibar mav. Iesus fo, Judas g…®n a is…® apanibar dafarim dat…®ght…® me a m…®sueght…®, an aremegham. 
\c 7  
\s1 Judabar Averpenibar Isar Ekiam…®n Dughiam otoz…®, Iesus an ganasa zui 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus Galilin Distrigh…®n aven arui. A fo, Judaba a m…®sueght…®ma an aremeghasa egha a bagha m…®zuai. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, a ua Judian Distrigh…®n mangan aghua.  
\v 2 Ez…® Judabar Averpenibar Isar Ekiam…®n Dughiam otivasa rogh…®ra izi.  
\v 3 Ez…® an doziba kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® danganir kam ategh…®va egh Judian Distrigh…®n mang…®. Eght…® n…®n suren gumaziba ingangarir n…® amibar ganam.  
\v 4 Egh gumazitam gumazamiziba bar a g…®foghs…®, a modogh ingangarim damuan kogham. Egh n…® bizir kabar amuava, kamagh…®n n…® uab…® is…® gumaziba bar men akagham.‚Äù  
\v 5 (An doziba uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®, egha akar kam m…®keme.) 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúNan dughiam a t…®ghar izam. Ez…® dughiaba bar, ian dughiar aghuiba.  
\v 7 Ez…® nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamiziba me ian apanim damuan kogham. Ez…® k…® men arazir kurar me amibar gun m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me nan apanim gami.  
\v 8 Ia uarira isam…®n dughiar kam bagh Jerusalem…®n mang…®. Eght…® k…®, nan dughiam t…®ghar izam, kamagh…®n, k…® isam…®n dughiam…®n mang…®ghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 9 A kamagh…®n me m…®kemegha, egha a Galilin Distrigh…®n ikiav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® an doziba ghuegha g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus uaghan g…®n zui. An azenara zuir puvat…®, a mogomebar zui, ez…® gumazamiziba a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 11 Ez…® isar ekiam…®n dughiam…®n, Judabar gumazir ekiaba a bagha garagharui, egha m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam managh iti?‚Äù  
\v 12 Ez…® gumazamiziba uarir tong…®n a bagha sighsirakaba uariv gei. Marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúA gumazir bar aghuim.‚Äù Ez…® marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®, a gumazamizibagh ifari.‚Äù  
\v 13 Egha me Judabar gumazir ekiabar atiati. Kamagh…®n amiz…® tav an araziba azenara dav geir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® isam…®n dughiar kam…®n tong…®n, Iesus God…®n d…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n aven ghugha egha gumazamizibar sure gami.  
\v 15 Judaba an akar kam barasi, egha me n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua egha m…®gei, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…® gumazir kam fofozir kaba iti? A suren ghuzir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® ia gan…®ngizir akar kam, kar nan akam puvat…®, kar God…®n akam, a na amadaz…®ma k…® ize.  
\v 17 Ez…® gumazitam God…®n akam bar an g…®n mangasa ifonge, an akar k…® m…®kemezir kam…®n m…®ngarim bar a g…®fogham. Egh a fogham, akar kam God…®n ize, o a pura nan n…®ghn…®zim…®n ize.  
\v 18 Gumazir pura uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n m…®geim, a uab…® uan ziam fasa ifonge. Ez…® gumazim a gumazir anemadazim…®n ziam fasa ifonge, gumazir kam a guiz…®n akabara m…®gei, egha a bizitam gifarir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄúFom…®ra Moses God…®n Araziba osirigha ia gan…®ngi. Egha gumazitam ian tong…®n ikia Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ia tizim bagh na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazamiziba an akam kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúTi duar kuratam n…® gapasa! Gumazir manamra n…® m…®sueght…® na aremegham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® mirakel…®n ingangarir vam…®ra a gami, ez…® ia bar n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami.\f + \ft (7:21) Iesus faragha Betesdan mozir d…®pam…®n borogh…®n ikia mirakel…®n kam gamigha, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n a m…®gei. N…® Jon 5:1-18…®n gan. Egha Kisim Bek 31:14-15…®n gan.\f* 
\v 22 Ez…® ia n…®ghn…®gh, Moses m…®karzir mogomem aghorir arazim ia gan…®ngi, ez…® ia Sabat…®n dughiabar uaghan otaribar m…®karzir mogomebar ghori. (Guizbang…®ra, Moses uab…® arazir kam at…®zir puvat…®. Arazir kam ian ovavibar oto.)  
\v 23 Ia Moses Osirizir Araziba deragh a dar g…®n mang…®s…®, egh ia Sabat…®n dughiam…®n otaribar m…®karzibar ghoram. Ez…® k…® gumazir mam Sabat…®n dughiam…®n a gamiz…®ma a ua bar dera, ez…® manmagh sua ia nan an…®ngaghe?\f + \ft (7:23) Moses Osirizir Araziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, amizitam otaritam batez…®mrama, me an g…®rara dughiabar bora, egha dughiar namba 8…®n me otarim…®n m…®karzir mogomem aghori. N…® gans…®, Wok Pris 12:3…®n gan. Iesus…®n dughiam…®n, me Sabat…®n dughiam…®n ingangaribar anogoroke. Eght…® otaritam…®n m…®karzir mogomem aghoramin dughiam Sabat…®n dughiatam…®n otogham, me ingangarir kam damuam. Me ghaze, m…®karzir mogomem aghorir arazim uaghan ingangarir mam, egha me guizbang…®ra ingangarir kam Sabat…®n dughiam uaghan a gami.\f* 
\v 24 Ia pura damazir k…®nibar bizibar gan…®va, da tuis…®ghan mark…®. Ia guiz…®n arazim…®n araziba derav…®ra da tuis…®gh.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazamiziba foghasa, Iesus a tinara 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Jerusalem…®n gumazamizir maba Iesus amizir bizibar ganigha egha m…®gei, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? Kar gumazir kamra, en gumazir ekiaba a m…®sueght…®ma an aremeghasa, me ifonge.  
\v 26 A kara, an azenara m…®gei, ez…® me m…®g…®r…®g…®atam a gamir puvat…®. Me ti fo, a gumazir kam, God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim?  
\v 27 Ez…® e gumazir kam…®n nguibam g…®fo. Eght…® God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim otoght…®, gumazitam an nguibam g…®foghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus God…®n D…®penim…®n ikia egha akam gumazamizibav k…®ri. Egha a kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúIa ghaze, ia ti bar na g…®fo, egha ia nan nguibar k…® izezim g…®fos, o? Ez…®, k…® uab…® uan ifongiam…®n izezir puvat…®. Afeziar na amadazim, an akam bar guizbang…®ra. Ez…® ia a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 29 Ez…® k…® a g…®fo. K…® a ko itima, a na amadaz…®ma ez…® k…® ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Me akar kam baregha egha a is…® kalabus dar…®ghasa. Ez…® an dughiam t…®ghar, kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazitam an suirazir puvat…®.  
\v 31 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rim me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia, egha me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezim otogh…®va, a mirakel…®n av…®ribar amut…® da mirakel…®n gumazir kam amibagh afiragham ti?‚Äù 
\s1 Me God…®n D…®penim…®n garir plisba amangiz…® me Iesus kalabus dar…®ghasa izi 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® Farisiba me gumaziba barazima me sighsirakaba Iesus amizir bizibav gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ko, God…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, me plis…®n gumaziba amadaz…®ma me Iesus…®n suighasa izi. 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar bar oveghevezim…®n k…® ia ko ikiam, egh k…® uamategh Afeziar na amadazim bagh mangam.  
\v 34 Eght…® ia nguibar k…® ikiamim…®n mang…®ghan kogham. Kamagh…®n ia na buriam, egh nan apighan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Ez…® Judaba uarir tong…®n uarira uariv m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA managh mang…®t…® eght…® e an ganighan kogham? A ti en gumazamizir kantri Grigh…®n itiba bagh mang…®gham, egh Grigh…®n gumazamizibar sure damuam, o?  
\v 36 A ghaze, ‚ÄòIa na buriva, egh ia nan apighan kogham.‚Äô Egha ghaze, ‚ÄòIa nguibar k…® ikiamim ia an mang…®gham kogham.‚Äô Ez…® akar kam…®n m…®ngarim manmak…®n?‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus, d…®par ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim, an a m…®gei 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…® isar ekiam…®n dughiar abuananam, a dughiar bar ekiam. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Iesus tugha egha pamten diagha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam kuarim an p…®ri, a na bagh iz…® egh d…®pam ramam.  
\v 38 Akar God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim, a d…®par ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim, an navir averiam giz…®vagh…®va, egh fasfagh iram.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \ft (7:38) God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven, akar otevir mam, akar Iesus vez…®n kam…®n m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, akar kam ko, aning magh ghuzir puvat…®. N…® Aisaia 44:3 ko Sindaun 18:4…®n gan.\f* 
\v 39 Iesus God…®n Duam m…®gei, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itiba, me a iniam. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Iesus ziar ekiam t…®ghar a iniam, kamak…®n God…®n Duam t…®ghar izam. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba uari ab…®ki 
\p  
