\v 53 \f * \ft (7:53-8:11) Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, akar m…®kovezir pumuning (*) tong…®n itim, Jon uab…® an osirizir puvat…®. Gumazir igharazim g…®n an osiri. N…® Jon 8:13 ko Lo 19:15…®n gan.\f* Ez…® gumazamiziba bar uan 
