\v 21 Egha Iesus ua gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® zui. Ia na buriva nan apighan kogham. Ian arazir kuraba ik…®v…®ra ikiam, eght…® ia aremegham. Egh ia k…® mangamin danganim, ia an mangan kogham.‚Äù 
