\c 9  
\s1 Gumazir damazir okav…®r…®zim…®n eghaghanim 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus ghuavigha gumazir damazir okav…®zir mam…®n api. An damazimning okaviz…® amebam a bate.  
\v 2 Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba an azara. ‚ÄúTisa, tina arazir kuram gami, gumazir kam o an amebam ko afeziam, ez…® kamagh…®n an damaziba okaviz…® amebam a bate?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir kam arazir kuram gamizir puvat…®, egha an amebam ko afeziam uaghan arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®. God kamagh sua, bizir gumazir kam…®n otozim, gumazamiziba an gan…®va fogham, God…®n ingangarim azenara men oto. Kamagh…®n an damaziba okaviz…® amebam a bate.  
\v 4 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n aruem ikiav…®ra itima, e gumazir na amadaz…® k…® izezim an ingangarim damuam. Am…®nim p…®rasava rogh…®ra izi, ez…® gumaziba ingangaritam damighan kogham.  
\v 5 Dughiar k…® nguazir kam…®n itim, k…® gumazir angazangarim nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibagh an…®dim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®kemegha egha nguazim giparigha egha nguazim sara veregha, egha gumazim…®n damazim gat…®.  
\v 7 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®va Siloam…®n mozir d…®pam guruegh.‚Äù (Ziar kam Siloam, an m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúAmada.‚Äù) Ez…® gumazir damazir okav…®r…®zim ghua rue. Egha uamategha iza, biziba bar derav…®ra dar gari. 
\p  
\v 8 Gumazir kam faragha dag…®aba uab…® dan…®ngasa gumazamizibagh inge, ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba an gani. Dat…®r…®gh…®n men marazi ko an borogh…®n itir darazi, me ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kamra, a faragha apiav ikia dag…®aba bagha gumazibagh inge?‚Äù  
\v 9 Egha marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, gumazir kamra.‚Äù Ez…® marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. A gumazir kam…®n m…®rara gara, egha a ighara.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam uab…® ghaze, ‚ÄúKar k…®rara.‚Äù  
\v 10 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…®ma n…®n damazimning dera?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® a kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir kam an ziam Iesus, a nguazim ko d…®pam veregha nan damazimning gat…®. Egha na m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® Siloam…®n mozir d…®pam…®n mang…®gh egh ruegh.‚Äô Ez…® k…® ghua ruez…®ma nan damazimning dera, ez…® k…® derav…®ra bizibar gari.‚Äù  
\v 12 Ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúGumazir kam managh iti?‚Äù Ez…® a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fozir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Egha me gumazir faragha damaziba okav…®zir kam me a inigha Farisiba bagha zui.  
\v 14 Ez…® dughiar Iesus nguazir beghneazim…®n ingarigha gumazim…®n damazimning gamiz…® a garim, kar Sabat…®n dughiam.  
\v 15 Ez…® kamagh…®n Farisiba uam an azai, ‚ÄúN…®n damazimning manmagh…®n amigha dera?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúA nguazir beghneazim isa nan damazimning gat…®z…®, ez…® k…® rue, egha k…® biziba derav…®ra dar gari.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Farisin maba ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam a Sabat…®n dughiam…®n arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n e fo, God gumazir kam amadaz…® puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…® gumazir arazir kuram itim mirakel…®n kabar amigham.‚Äù Egha me uari ab…®ki. 
\p  
\v 17 Egha Farisiba ua faragha gumazir damaziba okav…®zir kam…®n azangs…®si, ‚ÄúN…® ghaze, gumazir kam n…®n damazimning ak…®ri, ez…® kamagh…®n n…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, a gumazir manmagh…®ra garim?‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam kamagh…®n me akam ikara, ‚ÄúA God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Bar guizbang…®ra, faragha gumazir kam…®n damazimning okafi, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n an damazimning kuiaghir…®. Ez…® Judan gumazir aruaba bizir kam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikian aghua. Egha kamagh…®n me gumazir kam…®n amebam ko afeziam…®n diagha ghaze, gua iz…®.  
\v 19 Ez…® aning izima me kamagh…®n aning…®n azai, ‚ÄúKa ti guan borimra? Dughiar amebam a batezim, an damazimning okavigha iti, gua kamagh…®n m…®keme, o? Ez…® manmagh amiz…®ma a dat…®r…®gh…®n gari?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® an amebam ko afeziam kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúGa fo, kar gan borim. Ez…® dughiar amebam a batezim, an damazimning okavigha iti, ga uaghan a g…®fo.  
\v 21 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an damazimning manmagh…®n kuiaghir…®, ga uaghan fozir puvat…®. Ez…® tina an damazimning kui, ga uaghan fozir puvat…®. Ia an azaragh. An asegha g…®fa. A uab…® ua bagh m…®k…®mam.‚Äù  
\v 22 An amebam ko afeziam Judabar atiatigha, egha kamagh…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gami. Me fo, Judaba faragha kamagh…®n akam m…®soke, gumazitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúIesus a Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir kam,‚Äù eght…® me an anogoreght…® a ua God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ikian kogham.  
\v 23 Ez…® kamagh…®n gumazir kam…®n amebam ko afeziam ghaze, ‚ÄúAn asegha g…®fa. Ia an azangs…®gh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Egha g…®n me ua gumazir faragha damaziba okav…®zim dia, egha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n damazim…®n guiz…®n akam m…®k…®ms…® egh akar d…®k…®r…®zim damigh. E fo, gumazir n…® m…®kemezir kam, an arazir kurabagh amir gumazim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Egha a kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúAn arazir kurabagh amir gumazim o puvat…®, k…® kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®. Egha bizir vam…®ra, k…® a g…®fo, k…® faragha damazimning okafi, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n nan damazimning kuiaghir…®.‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® me uam an azara, ‚ÄúA manmagh…®n n…® gami? A manmagh…®n n…®n damazimning ak…®ri?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® a kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®kemegha g…®fa, ez…® ia oraghan aghua. Ia manmagh sua dughiar av…®ribar oraghasa? Ia ti uaghan an suren gumazibar otivasa, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Farisiba d…®bovibar kamagh…®n gumazir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®rara an suren gumazim. E Moses…®n suren gumaziba.  
\v 29 E kamagh…®n fo, God akam Moses gan…®ngi. Ez…® gumazir kam, e fozir puvat…®, a nguibar manam…®n oto.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® gumazir faragha damaziba okav…®zir kam, a kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúIa akar bar igharazim m…®geima, k…® d…®gavir kuram gami! Gumazir nan damazimning ak…®rizir kam, ia ghaze ia g…®fozir puvat…®, a nguibar manam…®n oto.  
\v 31 E fo, God gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba barazir puvat…®. Gumazitam God…®n ziam f…®va egh an ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, eght…® God a baragham.  
\v 32 Bar fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®k…®n, gumazitam…®n damazimning okaviz…® amebam a batez…®, ez…® g…®n gumazir mam an damazimning ak…®riz…®, e eghaghanir katam e a baraghizir puvat…®.  
\v 33 God gumazir kam amadaghan koghai, a bizitam damighan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Farisiba me akar kam baregha egha kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúManmagh ami? Arazir kuram bar n…® avara, dughiar n…®n amebam n…® batezim…®n tugha egha iza dat…®r…®k…®n. Ez…® n…® ti en sure damuasa, o?‚Äù Egha me a batoghez…®ma a zui. 
\s1 Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir puvat…®ziba, me mati men damaziba okafi 
\p  
\v 35 Iesus orazima me gumazir kam batoke, ez…® a ghua a buri. Egha a batogha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Gumazibar Otarim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ti, o puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® a kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, Gumazibar Otarir kam a tina? K…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®s…®, kamagh…®n n…® na m…®k…®m, a tina.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® an ganigha g…®fa. A gumazir dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® ko m…®geim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® gumazir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti.‚Äù Egha Iesus…®n guam…®n tevimning ap…®righa an ziam fe. 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®ghasa k…® ize. K…® kamagh sua, gumazir damaziba okavigha itiba me ganam, ez…® gumazir gariba, men damaziba okavigham. Bizir kam bagha, k…® nguazir kam…®n ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 40 Farisin maba me Iesus…®n borogh…®ra ikia akar kam baraki. Egha an azara, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n e m…®k…®masa, e ti uaghan damaziba okafi, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan damaziba okaviz…®, ia arazir kurabar os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®ghai. Egha ia ghaze, ‚ÄòEn damaziba gari.‚Äô Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ian arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\c 10  
\s1 Iesus, a sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazir aghuim 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra k…® ia m…®gei, gumazim sipsipbar d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n aven zuir puvat…®gha, egha tuavir igharazim…®n d…®vazim…®n ikiavk…®nigha egha aven ghua, a mati ok…®mak…®ar gumazim egha gumazir igharaz darazir biziba isim.  
\v 2 Ez…® gumazir tiar akam…®n aven zuim, a sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazim.  
\v 3 Tiar akam…®n garir gumazim a gumazir kam bagha tiam kui. Ez…® sipsipba an tiarim barasi. Ez…® a vaghvagha uab…® uan sipsipbar ziabar diava egha men akua azenan zui.  
\v 4 A uan sipsipbar akua azenan ghugha, egha a uab…® men faragha zui. Ez…® sipsipba an tiarim barasi. Kamagh…®n me an g…®n zui.  
\v 5 Me gumazir igharazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Me gumazir igharazibar tiaribagh fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n ami, gumazir igharazim men d…®mt…®, sipsipba an aregham.‚Äù  
\v 6 Iesus akar is…®n zuim…®n me m…®keme, ez…® me akar kam…®n m…®ngarim, me a g…®fozir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Iesus ua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, k…® uab…®, k…® sipsipba aven zuir tiar akam.  
\v 8 Gumazir nan faragha izeziba, me bar ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba egha gumazibar biziba isir gumaziba. Ez…® sipsipba me barazir puvat…®.  
\v 9 K…® uab…® k…® tiar akam. Ez…® gumazitam na bagh iz…®va egh d…®vazim…®n aven mang…®ght…®, God an akurvagham. Eght…® an aven mang…®gh…®va egh azenan izam, egh daruva dagheba iniam. 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúOk…®mak…®ar gumazim, a sipsipba ok…®m…®va me m…®soght…®ma me ar…®m…®ghiram, egh me gas…®ghas…®ghasa izi. A bizir igharazitam damuasa izir puvat…®. Ez…® ko, k…® ia angamra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim iniasa, k…® ize, eght…® ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim guizbang…®ra ia giz…®vagham. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazir aghuim. Egha sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazir aghuim, a uan sipsipbar akurvaghs…® me bagh aremegham.  
\v 12 Ez…® gumazir dag…®ar ingangarimra amim, a guizbang…®ra sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazim puvat…®, a sipsipbar ghuavim puvat…®. Egha a sipsipbar garima afiar atiar mam izima, a sipsipba ategh ar…®mang…®gham. Eght…® afiar atiam sipsipbar am…®va egh men ag…®nt…®ght…® me tintinibar mangegham.  
\v 13 Gumazir kam uan ivezim iniasav…®ra ingara iti. A guizbang…®ra sipsipbagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, a sipsipba ategh ar…®mang…®gham. 
\p  
\v 14-15 ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazir aghuim. Afeziam na g…®foz…®ma, k…® Afeziam g…®foz…® mogh…®ra k…® uan sipsipbagh fo, ez…® nan sipsipba na g…®fo. Ez…® k…® sipsipbar akurvaghs…®, me bagh aremegham.  
\v 16 K…® sipsip…®n maba uaghan iti, da d…®vazir kam…®n sipsipba puvat…®. Ez…® k…® sipsip…®n kaba uaghan men aku izam, eght…® me nan tiarim baragham. Egh…®va me bar sipsip…®n okuruar vam…®ra ik…®t…®, eght…® sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazir vam…®ra bar me geghuvam. 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúK…® kamagh sua, k…® ua d…®kavigh angamra ikiam, kamagh…®n k…® aremeghasa ifonge. Kamagh…®n ami, Afeziam bar na gifonge.  
\v 18 Gumazitam na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® uab…® nan ifongiam…®n k…® aremegham. K…® oveghamin gavgavim ikia, egha uaghan ua d…®kavamin gavgavim iti. Nan Afeziam kamagh…®n damuasa na m…®keme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Judaba akar kam baregha egha ua uari tuiragha okoroar pumuning iti.  
\v 20 Egha gumazir av…®riba ghaze, ‚ÄúDuar kuram a gapasa, ez…® an ongani. Manmagh sua ia an akam barasi?‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…® marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúAkar kam, a duar kuram gapazazir gumazim…®n akam puvat…®. Eght…® duar kuram manmagh…®n gumazir damazim okav…®zim ak…®righam?‚Äù 
\s1 Judaba me Iesus…®n apanim…®n iti 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, isar ekiam…®n dughiam Jerusalem…®n oto. Kar dughiar me fom…®ra God…®n D…®penim g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, d…®penir kam a God baghav…®ra itir d…®penim. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me dughiar kam gin…®ghn…®si. An orangt…®zim…®n dughiam…®n oto.  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus God…®n D…®penim…®n ikia Solomon…®n Azuarim…®n aven arui.  
\v 24 Ez…® Judaba iza anekuvagha egha kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúDughiar manamra n…® derav…®ra e m…®k…®mam, n…® bar tinara? N…® gumazir kamra, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, egh n…® derav…®ra e m…®k…®m.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®kemegha g…®fa, ez…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikian aghua. K…® ingangariba bar uan Afeziam…®n ziam…®n dagh ami, ez…® ingangarir kaba nan gun m…®g…®a ian akakasi, k…® tinara.  
\v 26 Egha ia nan sipsipba puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itir puvat…®.  
\v 27 Nan sipsipba nan tiarim barasi, ez…® k…® me g…®foz…®, me nan g…®n izi.  
\v 28 K…® zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim me gan…®di, eght…® me ovengan kogham. Bar puvat…®. Eght…® gumazitam nan dafarim…®n me batueghan kogham.  
\v 29 Nan Afeziam me isa na gan…®ngi. Egha an gavgavim bar ekevegha, bizir igharazibar gavgaviba, bar dagh afira. Kamagh…®n amiz…® gumazitam an dafarim…®n me batueghan kogham.  
\v 30 Ez…® k…® uan Afeziam ko, ga gumazir vam…®ran m…®n iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Judaba akar kam baregha egha me ua a ginivasa dag…®aba isi.  
\v 32 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan Afeziam na m…®kemez…®, k…® ingangarir aghuir av…®ribagh amima ia dar gani. Egha, ia ingangarir kabar manamra n…®ghn…®gha egha dag…®aba na ginivasa?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúE ingangarir aghuitam g…®n…®ghn…®gha egha dag…®aba f…® n…® m…®k…®nasa, puvat…®. N…® God…®n danganim iniasa, kamagh…®n e dag…®aba n…® m…®k…®nasa. N…® pura gumazir k…®nim, egha n…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® uab…® n…® God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúIan Arazir Moses Osirizim…®n aven, akar kam iti, ‚ÄòGod ghaze, ‚ÄúIarara godba.‚Äù ‚Äô  
\v 35 Fom…®ra God akar kam…®n gun gumazibav keme, egha me m…®g…®a ghaze, me godba. Ez…® e fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akam zurara ik…®v…®ra ik…®va, igharagha otoghan kogham.  
\v 36 Ez…® ko, Afeziam uab…® na m…®sefe, egha na amadaz…®ma k…® nguazim…®n ize. Egha k…® ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® God…®n Otarim,‚Äô ez…® manmagh sua ia ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n danganim iniasa?‚Äô 
\p  
\v 37 ‚ÄúK…® uan Afeziam…®n ingangarim damuan koght…®, eght…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan akam…®n ikian mark…®.  
\v 38 Ez…® k…® an ingangarim gami. Ez…® ia nan akam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikian aghuagh…®va, egh ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ingangarir k…® amibar ik…®. Eght…® ia derav…®ra fofoziba ko n…®ghn…®ziba kamagh…®n da ini, Afeziam nan aven iti, ez…® k…® Afeziam…®n aven iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Egha me uam an suighasava amima, ez…® a men tong…®n suiaghr…®gha ghu. 
\p  
\v 40 Egha Iesus uamategha ghua Jordan…®n d…®pam abigha vong…®n ghu. Egha ghua danganir Jon fom…®ra gumaziba ruezim…®n oto, egha a danganir kam…®n iti.  
\v 41 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba a bagha izi. Egha me ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, Jon gavgavim uan akam dan…®ngasa mirakel…®n arazitam gamizir puvat…®. Egha akar Jon gumazir kam…®n gun m…®kemeziba, da bar guizbang…®ra.‚Äù  
\v 42 Ez…® dughiar Iesus danganir kam…®n itim, gumazamizir av…®riba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. 
\c 11  
\ms1 Iesus Judian Distrigh ko Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n ghuz…®ma, gumazir aruaba a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa 
\mr (Sapta 11-12) 
\s1 Lasarus aremegha g…®fa 
\p  
\v 1 Gumazir mam Lasarus, an arei. A Betanin nguibam…®n gumazim. Betanin nguibam, Maria uan avenamebam Marta aning itir nguibam.\f + \ft (11:1) Maria ko Marta, aning Lasarus…®n amizimning.\f* 
\v 2 (Marian kamra, a mughuriar aghuim zuir borem isa Ekiam…®n dagarimning ginge, egha uan dapanir ar…®zibar aned…®si. Dat…®r…®gh…®n an dozim Lasarus arei.)  
\v 3 Ez…® an amizimning Iesus bagha akam amada, ‚ÄúEkiam, gumazir n…® bar ifongezim, an arei.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus oregha, egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar gumazim aremegh bar g…®vaghamin ar…®mariam puvat…®. Kar gumazamizibar amut…® me God…®n gavgavim…®n gan…®va egh ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam. Ez…® tuavir kamra, God…®n Otarim uaghan ziar ekiam iniam.‚Äù  
\v 5 Iesus bar Marta ko an afumim ko Lasarus, me gifonge.  
\v 6 Ez…® a Lasarus…®n ar…®mariam…®n akam baregha, egha ua dughiar pumuning…®n nguibar a itir kam…®n ikiav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 7 Egha a g…®n suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúE uamategh Judian Distrigh…®n mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® suren gumaziba a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúTisa, bogh…®mra Judian Distrigh…®n itir gumaziba, me dag…®aba f…® n…® m…®k…®nasava ami. Ez…® n…® uamategh Judian Distrigh…®n mangasa, a?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúDughiar vam…®ra aruem ti 12 plan auan gari, o? Gumazim aruem…®n aruava, nguazir kam…®n angazangarim…®n garava, kamagh…®n an asaghpora irir puvat…®.  
\v 10 Ez…® gumazim d…®magarim…®n aruava, a ganamin angazangariba puvat…®, kamagh…®n an asaghpor ir…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®g…®a, egha g…®n ua me m…®gei, ‚ÄúEn roroam Lasarus an akui. Ez…® k…® mang…®va a damight…® a d…®kavigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® suren gumaziba akar kam baregha egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, a dakuigh…®va, an ar…®mariam g…®vagham.‚Äù  
\v 13 Suren gumaziba me kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, Iesus ghaze, Lasarus aremegha g…®fa. Me ghaze, Iesus Lasarus…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, a puram akui. 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Iesus derav…®ra kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúLasarus an aremegha g…®fa.  
\v 15 Ez…® k…® ia gin…®ghn…®si, egha k…® fo, bizir kam ia damut…®, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikiam. Kamagh…®n, k…® a ko dughiar kam…®n ikezir puvat…®gha, egha k…® bar akonge. Egh dat…®r…®gh…®n, e a bagh mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
