\v 48 E kamagh…®n aneteght…® an arazir kam damuv…®ra ik…®t…®, eght…® gumazamiziba bar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam. Eght…® Rom…®n gumazir ekiaba iz…®va en God…®n D…®penim ko en adarasi saram as…®ghasigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 49 Ez…® men tong…®n gumazir mam, an ziam Kaiafas, an azenir kam…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim. A kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa fofoziba bar puvat…®.  
