\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúDughiar Gumaziba Otarim ziar ekiam iniamim, an otogha g…®fa.  
\v 24 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, wit…®n ov…®zitam nguazim gir…®gh egh aremeghan kogh…®va, a uab…®ra ikiam. Egh an aremegh, a uam aghung…®va egh wit…®n ov…®zir av…®riba m…®s…®vam.  
\v 25 Gumazir uab…®ra uan m…®karzim gifongezim, an aremegham. Ez…® gumazir nguazir kam…®n ikia uab…® uan m…®karzim aghuazim, an angamra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n suiragh mang…® zurara ik…®v…®ra ikiam.  
\v 26 Ez…® gumazir nan ingangarim damuasa ifongezim, a nan g…®n iz…®. Egh nguibar k…® itim, nan ingangarir gumazim uaghan na ko ikiam. Ez…® gumazir nan ingangarim gamim, Afeziam ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus uan ovevem m…®gei 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n nan navim bar osemegha n…®ghn…®zir av…®riba iti. Egha k…® manmagh m…®k…®mam? K…® ti kamagh m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòAfeziam, n…® bizir na bativamim batokegh?‚Äô Puvat…®. K…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham. Os…®mt…®zir dughiar kam…®n otivim, a na bativam. Bizir kam bagha k…® ize.  
\v 28 Afeziam n…® uan ziam damut…®, an ekefegh!‚Äù 
\p Iesus m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® tiarir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n zaghira ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® uan ziam gamiz…®ma an ekevegha g…®fa, eght…® k…® ua kamagh…®n damuam.‚Äù  
\v 29 Ez…® gumazamizir rogh…®ra tughav itiba, me tiarir kam baraki, egha me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúArarim dagara!‚Äù Ez…® marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúEnsel…®n mam a m…®gei!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúAkar ia dat…®r…®gh…®n oraghazir kam, a nan akurvaghasa izezir puvat…®. A ian akurvaghasa ize.  
\v 31 Dat…®r…®gh…®n God nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®gham. Egh nguazir kam gativazir gumazir dapanim Satan a batuegham.  
\v 32 Dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® nguazim…®n iti, ez…® g…®n me na fegh ter ighuvim…®n na aguragham, eght…® dughiar kam…®n k…® gumazamiziba bar me damut…® me na bagh izam.‚Äù\f + \ft (12:32) Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúGumaziba na fegh ter ighuvim…®n na aguragham.‚Äù Tuavir kamra, God a feght…® an an Nguibam…®n mang…®, egh bar p…®n ikiam. N…® Filipai 2:9-11…®n gan.\f* 
\v 33 (Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gamua egha arazir an ovengamim…®n gun m…®gei.) 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúE kamagh…®n Moses Osirizir Arazibar akam baraki, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim otogh, egh a ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Egha manmagh sua n…® ghaze, ‚ÄòMe Gumazibar Otarim fegh ter ighuvim…®n aneguragham?‚Äô Gumazibar Otarir kam, a bar tinara?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar ovezim…®n angazangarim ian tong…®n ikiam. Dat…®r…®gh…®n angazangarim ian ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® ia angazangarim…®n aven daru. Puvat…®ght…®, m…®tatem ia avaragham. E fo, gumazim m…®tatem…®n arui, a fozir puvat…®, a managh zui.  
\v 36 Angazangarim dat…®r…®gh…®n ia ko ikiav…®ra iti, eght…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim angazangarim…®n ik…®. Kamagh…®n ia angazangarim…®n gumazamizibar m…®n otivigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Judan gumazir av…®rim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir puvat…® 
\p Iesus gumazamiziba ko m…®kemegha g…®vagha, egha me ategha ghua men modo.  
\v 37 Me an garima a mirakel…®n av…®rim gami. Ez…® me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®.  
