\q3 Egha men n…®ghn…®zibagh amiz…® me ongani.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 41 Aisaia Iesus…®n angazangarim ko gavgavim…®n ganigha, kamagh…®n an an gurara m…®gei.  
\v 42 Guizbang…®ra, gumazir dapanir av…®rim uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n iti. Egha me Farisibar atiatigha, egha uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n gun m…®geir puvat…®. Me atiatigha ghaze, Farisiba men anogoreght…® me ua God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ikian kogham.  
\v 43 Gumaziba men ziaba fasa me bar ifonge, egha God men ziaba fasa me ifongezir puvat…®. 
\s1 Akar Iesus m…®kemezim, a gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®gham 
\p  
\v 44 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim narara itir puvat…®. A n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Afeziar na amadaz…® k…® izezim uaghan an iti.  
\v 45 Ez…® gumazir nan garim, a uaghan Afeziar na amadaz…® k…® izezim…®n gari.  
\v 46 K…® kamagh sua, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itiba, me bar m…®tatem…®n ikian kogham. Bizir kam bagha k…® angazangarim…®n m…®n nguazir kam…®n ize. 
\p  
\v 47 ‚ÄúGumazitam nan akam baregha egha nan g…®n zuir puvat…®, k…® jas…®n m…®n a tuis…®ghan kogham. K…® nguazim…®n gumazamizibar jas…®n ikiasa izezir puvat…®. K…® men akurvaghasa ize.  
\v 48 Ez…® gumazim ak…®rim na gasara egha nan akam inizir puvat…®, a kot iti, eght…® jas a tuis…®gham. Akar k…® m…®kemezim, a nguazim g…®vaghamin dughiam…®n an an araziba tuis…®gham.  
\v 49 K…® uab…® uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n m…®geir puvat…®. Afeziam na amadaz…® k…® ize. A uab…® akaba bar na m…®keme, ez…® k…® dar gun m…®gei.  
\v 50 Ez…® k…® fo, Afeziam…®n akam a gumazamizibagh amima, eght…® g…®n me zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. Kamagh…®n ami, akar k…® m…®kemezir kaba bar, k…® Afeziam na m…®kemez…® mogh…®n k…® dagh ami.‚Äù 
\c 13  
\ms1 Iesus kamagh…®n suren gumazibav m…®g…®a ghaze, a me ategh ua Afeziam bagh mangam 
\mr (Sapta 13-17) 
\s1 Iesus uan suren gumazibar dagariba rue 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar kam, God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam a gurum…®zaraghan otivam. Ez…® Iesus fo, a mangamin dughiam otoz…®, a nguazir kam ategh uan Afeziam bagh mangasava ami. A uan gumazamizir nguazir kam…®n itiba a fom…®ra bar me gifonge, egha me g…®fueghav…®ra ikia ghua an areme.  
\v 2 Ez…® guarat…®zir kam…®n me apa iti. Satan faragha n…®ghn…®zir Iesus is…® apanibar agharim dar…®ghamim isa Judas…®n navim gat…®gha g…®fa. Judas, a Saimon Iskariot…®n otarim.  
\v 3 Iesus kamagh…®n fo, Afeziam bizibar amuamin gavgavim bar a isa a gan…®ngi. A uaghan kamagh…®n fo, God anemadaz…® a ize, egh a ua God bagh mangam.  
\v 4 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Iesus dagher dakozim ategha d…®kafi, egha uan korotiar ruarim suegha, egha taul…®n mam inigha uan ivariam ike.  
\v 5 Egha d…®pam itarir mam ginge, egha magh…®ra uan suren gumazibar dagariba ruegha, egha taul…®n a uan ivariam am…®gh…®rizim…®n da ad…®si.  
\v 6 Egha a Saimon Pita bagha ize. Ez…® Pita an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…®rara nan dagariba ruam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúBizir k…® amim, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n a g…®fozir puvat…®. Egh n…® g…®n a g…®fogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Pita a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan dagariba ruan mark…®. Bar mark…®!‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n dagariba rueghan koght…®ma, eght…® n…® na ko ikian kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Saimon Pita a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® kamagh…®n nan dagaribara ruan mark…®. N…® nan dagariba ko dafariba ko dapanim sara, bar da ruam!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ruegha g…®vazim, a zue, a ua ruan mark…®. A pura dagaribara ruegh egh bar zuegham. Ez…® ia bar mogh…®ra zuegha g…®vagha iti. Ez…® ian gumazir vam…®ra, a zuezir pu.‚Äù  
\v 11 (Iesus gumazir a is…® apanibar agharim dar…®ghamim, an a g…®fogha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bar mogh…®ra zuez…®, ez…® ian vav…®ra zuezir puvat…®.‚Äù) 
\p  
\v 12 Iesus men dagariba ruegha g…®vagha, egha uan korotiar ruarim uam anerugha egha ua ghua uan dapiamin danganim gapera. Egha kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúIa, k…® ia bagha amizir bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fo, o?  
\v 13 Ia ‚ÄòTisa‚Äô na gar…®gha egha ‚ÄòEkiam‚Äô na gar…®si. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Tisa egha k…® ian Ekiam. Egha bar deragha ia kamagh…®n m…®gei.  
\v 14 K…®, ian Ekiam ko ian Tisa, egha k…® ian dagariba rues. Ez…® ia uaghan uarira uarir dagariba ruegh.  
\v 15 K…® arazim ian akaz…®, ez…® ia uaghan arazir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gamizir kamra damu.  
\v 16 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ingangarir gumazir k…®nitam uan Ekiam gafirazir puvat…®. Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazitam, a gumazir anemadazir a ghuzim gafirazir puvat…®.  
\v 17 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia arazir k…® amizir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fogha g…®fa, kamagh…®n ia deraghv…®ra an g…®n mang…®va, egh ia bar akuegham. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúK…® bar ia m…®geir puvat…®. K…® gumazir k…® ua bagha m…®sevezibagh fo. Egha k…® kamagh…®n fo, akar God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itim, a guizbang…®ram otivam. Akar kam kamak…®n ‚ÄòGumazir na ko dagheba apim, nan apanim…®n oto.‚Äô  
\v 19 Bizir kam t…®ghar otivam, ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia m…®kemegha g…®fa. Eght…® kamagh…®n a g…®n otoghamin dughiam, ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® fogh, K…® Uab…® K…® Kamagh…®n Iti.\f + \ft (13:19) N…® akar Jon 8:24…®n itim…®n gan.\f* 
\v 20 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazir manam ingangarir gumazir k…® amadazim inigh, egha derav…®ra a gami, gumazir kam na inigha egha derav…®ra na gami. Egha gumazir na inizim, a God…®n na amadaz…® k…® izezim a ini.‚Äù 
\s1 Judas Iesus is…® apanibar agharim dar…®gham. 
\r (Matyu 26:20-25 ko Mak 14:17-20 ko Luk 22:21-23) 
\p  
\v 21 Iesus m…®kemegha g…®fa, ez…® an navim bar a baseme. Egha bighav…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ian tav na is…®va gumazir nan apanim gamibar agharim dar…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 A kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®, an suren gumaziba vaghvagha uari uarir gari. Me fozir puvat…®, Iesus tina m…®gei.  
\v 23 Egha suren gumazibar mav, gumazir Iesus bar ifongezim, a bar Iesus…®n borogh…®ra iti.  
\v 24 Ez…® Saimon Pita benim akuigha egha a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® an azaragh, a tina m…®gei?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® suren gumazir kam uan dapanim isa Iesus…®n afar…®zim borogh…®ram at…®gha, egha kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® tina m…®gei?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® dagher otevir kam inigh egh d…®pars…®zim darugh, egh gumazitam dan…®ngam. A gumazir kamra, k…® a m…®gei.‚Äù Egha a dagher otevim isa d…®pars…®zim garu, egha Judas gan…®ngi, a Saimon Iskariot…®n otarim.  
\v 27 Ez…® Judas dagher kam inigha g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® dughiar kamra Satan an navir averiam…®n aven ghua a gapasa. Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir n…® damuasa ifongezim, n…® zuam…®ra a damigh!‚Äù  
\v 28 Gumazir dakozim…®n apiaghav itiba, me bar akar Iesus Judas…®n m…®kemezir kam baregha, egha me akam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 29 Judas dag…®abar m…®tarim…®n gari. Ez…® marazi ghaze, Iesus ti isar ekiam bagha bizibagh ivezasa a m…®keme, o a mang…® biziba gumazir onganarazibar an…®ngam.  
\v 30 Ez…® Judas dagher otevir kam inigha g…®vagha, egha zuam…®ra azenan ghu. Ez…® am…®nim p…®riz…® m…®tatem otogha g…®fa. 
\s1 Iesus arazir igiam suren gumazibagh an…®di 
\p  
\v 31 Judas azenan ghugha g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n Gumazibar Otarim…®n ziar ekiam azenan oto. Ez…® God uan Otarim isa gumazamizibar akaz…® Otarim me damut…® me fogham, God ziar bar ekiam iti.  
\v 32 Eght…® God uab…® uan Otarim is…® gumazamizibar akaght…® me fogham, Gumazibar Otarim ziar ekiam iti. Egh God zuam…®ra a damigham.  
\v 33 Nan boriba, dughiar otevimra k…® ia ko ikiam. Eght…® ia na buriam. K…® Judabav m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, akar kamra k…® ua ia m…®gei, ia danganir k…® mangamim, ia an mangan kogham.  
\v 34 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® arazir igiam ia gan…®di, a kamak…®n, ia uari uarigh ifongegh. K…® bar ia gifonge, ez…® kamagh…®ra ia uari uarigh ifongegh.  
\v 35 Ia uari uarigh ifongeght…®, gumaziba bar arazir kam…®n ganigh fogh suam, ia nan suren gumaziba.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, Pita ak…®rim ragh a gasaragham 
\r (Matyu 26:31-35 ko Mak 14:27-31 ko Luk 22:31-34) 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® Saimon Pita kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® managh mangam?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúNguibar k…® mangamim, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan g…®n an mang…®ghan kogham. Egh n…® g…®n nan g…®n izam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…® Pita an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, manmagh amiz…®ma k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n g…®n mang…®ghan kogham? K…® n…® bagh aremeghasa ifonge.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúN…® ghaze, n…® ti na bagh aremegham? K…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, tuarim t…®ghar akegham, eght…® n…® dughiar pumuning…®n ko m…®kezim…®n kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, n…® na g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\c 14  
\s1 Iesus, an Afeziam bagha zuir tuavim 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus ua kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuva os…®man mark…®. Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®va, egh uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ik…®.  
\v 2 Nan Afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n danganir av…®riba iti, ez…® k…® mang…®va ia bagh danganibar k…®ram. Bizir kam guizbang…®ra puvat…®z…®, ez…® k…® ia m…®kemeghan koghai.  
\v 3 K…® mang…®va ia bagh danganim ak…®righ…®va, egh ua iz…® ia inigh mang…®t…® ia na ko ikiam. Egh nguibar k…® ikiamim, ia uaghan na ko an ikiam.  
\v 4 Ez…® ia nguibar k…® zuim, ia an tuavim g…®fogha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Tomas a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, e fozir pu, n…® managh zui, kamagh…®n e manmagh…®n tuavir n…® zuim g…®fogham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® tuavim, egha k…® guiz…®n akam…®n m…®ngarim, egha k…® ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim…®n m…®ngarim. Ez…® gumazitam tuavir igharazim…®n Afeziam bagh mang…®gham kogham. Puvat…®. K…®rara k…® Afeziam bagha zuir tuavim.  
\v 7 Eght…® ia na g…®fogh…®va, egh uaghan nan Afeziam g…®fogham. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n tugha ghua, ia nan Afeziam g…®fofogha, egha an gari.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Filip ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® Afeziam en akagh, eght…® e uan damazibar an ganika, eght…® e ua n…®n azangan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúFilip, dughiar ruarim…®n k…® ia ko iti, ez…® ia ti na g…®fozir puvat…®? Gumazim nan gari, an Afeziam…®n gari. Ez…® manmagh sua n…® ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® Afeziam en akagh‚Äô?  
\v 10 Filip, n…® ti n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® fogh suam, k…® Afeziam…®n aven itima Afeziam nan aven iti? Akar k…® ia m…®geiba, k…® uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n dav geir puvat…®. Afeziar nan aven itim, a uab…® uan ingangarim gami.  
\v 11 Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim akar kam…®n ik…®, k…® Afeziam…®n aven iti, ez…® Afeziam nan aven iti. Puvat…®ght…®, ia nan ingangarir k…® amibagh n…®ghn…®gh, eght…® ingangarir kaba ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar amut…® da gavgavigham.  
\v 12 K…® bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim, a uaghan k…® amir ingangarir kabar amuam. K…® uan Afeziam bagh mangam, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ingangarir ekiar gumazir kam damuamiba, da ingangarir k…® amibagh afiragham.  
\v 13 K…® kamagh sua, Afeziam ziar ekiam uan Otarim…®n ingangarim…®n a iniam. Kamagh…®n ia nan ziam…®n biziba bagha azaraght…®, k…® dar amuam.  
\v 14 Ia nan ziam…®n bizitam bagh nan azangs…®ght…®, k…® a damuam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, a God…®n Duam amadaght…® a izam 
\p  
\v 15 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar na gifuegh…®va, egh ia derav…®ra nan akaba baragh dar g…®n mangam.  
\v 16 Eght…® k…® Afeziam…®n azangs…®ght…®, a gavgavim ia dan…®ngamin Akurvazir mam ia bagh anemangam. Eght…® a ia ko ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 17 Ez…® Akurvazir kam a God…®n Duam, a guiz…®n akam m…®geir Duam. Ez…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba me an ganighan kogh…®va, egh a g…®foghan kogham, kamagh…®n me a inighan kogham. Ez…® iarara, a ia ko iti, egh a ian navir averiabar aven ikiam. Kamagh…®n ia a g…®fo. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúK…® ia ateght…® ia uarira ikian kogham, mati borim amebam ko afeziam puvat…®z…® mogh…®n. Puvat…®. K…® ua ia bagh izam.  
\v 19 Dughiar ovezim…®n nguazim…®n gumazamiziba ua nan ganan kogham. Eght…® ia nan ganam. K…® angamra iti, eght…® kamagh…®n ia uaghan angamra ikiam.  
\v 20 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n ia kamagh…®n fogham, k…® uan Afeziam…®n aven iti, ez…® ia nan aven iti, mati k…® ian aven iti mogh…®n.  
\v 21 Ez…® tina nan akam baragha egha an g…®n zui, gumazir kam a bar na gifonge. Egha gumazir na gifongezim, nan Afeziam a gifuegham. Eght…® k…® uaghan a g…®fuegham, egh k…® uab…® is…®va an akagham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®keme, ez…® Judas…®n igharazim (a Judas Iskariot puvat…®) a kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, manmagh su n…® uab…® is…®va en akaghasa, egha n…® uab…® is…®va nguazim…®n gumazamizibar akaghan aghua?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúGumazitam na gifuegh…®va, egh deraghv…®ra nan akam…®n g…®n mangam. Eght…® nan Afeziam bar gumazir kam gifuegham. Eght…® ga iz…®va a ko ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 24 Gumazim na gifongezir puvat…®, a derav…®ra nan akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ez…® akar ia oraghizir kam, ka nan akam puvat…®. Kar Afeziam…®n akam, a na amadaz…® ez…® k…® ize. 
\p  
\v 25 ‚ÄúDughiar k…® ia ko ikiav…®ra itim, k…® bizir kabar gun ia m…®keme.  
\v 26 Ez…® Gavgavim ia Dan…®ngamin Akurvazir Gumazim, a God…®n Duam. Ez…® nan ziam…®n, Afeziam anemadaght…® a izam. A biziba bar ian sure damuam. Eght…® akar k…® ia m…®kemeziba, a ian sure damut…® ia uam a dagh n…®ghn…®gham. 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄúK…® ia ataghraghasa, egha k…® navir am…®r…®zim ia gan…®di. Ez…® nan navir am…®r…®zir k…® ia gan…®dim, a nguazim…®n gumaziba an…®di mogh…®n puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuva egh os…®man mark…®, egh atiatingan mark…®.  
\v 28 Ez…® ia akar k…® ia gan…®ngizir kam baregha g…®fa, ‚ÄòK…® ia ategha egha k…® zui, egh k…® ua ia bagh izam.‚Äô Egh ia bar na gifueght…®, eght…® akar kam ia damut…® ia bar akuegham. Afeziam…®n gavgavim bar ekevegha egha nan gavgavim gafira, kamagh…®n, k…® uan Afeziam bagha zui.  
\v 29 K…® kamagh sua, bizir kam g…®n otoght…®, eght…® ia an ganigh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ik…®. Kamagh…®n k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir kam t…®ghar otivamin dughiam…®n, k…® an gun ia m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 30 ‚ÄúNguazir kam gativazir gumazir dapanim, a na gativamin gavgaviba puvat…®. Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n izi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ua m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®riba ia m…®k…®man kogham.  
\v 31 K…® kamagh sua, nguazim…®n gumazamiziba kamagh…®n fogh, k…® bar Afeziam gifonge, egha k…® bizir Afeziam na m…®kemezibara dagh ami. Ia d…®kavigh, danganir kam ategh, e mangam.‚Äù 
\c 15  
\s1 Iesus a guizbang…®ra wain…®n ikarzim…®n m…®n iti 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® guizbang…®ra wain…®n ikarzim…®n m…®n iti. Ez…® nan Afeziam a wain…®n azenim…®n ghuavim.  
\v 2 Ez…® nan agharir ber puvat…®ziba, Afeziam vaghavagha dar ghora da makuri. Egha agharir ov…®ziba itiba, Afeziam vaghavagha a dar ghora da otefi. A ghaze, da zuegh ik…®va, egh g…®n da b…®va ov…®zir av…®riba ikiam, kamagh…®n a dar ghori.  
\v 3 Ia zuegha g…®fa. Akar kam k…® ia gan…®di, a ia gamima ia zue.  
\v 4 Ia nan porogh, eght…® k…® ian porogham. Ez…® wain…®n ikarzim…®n agharim, a ikarzim…®n poroghan kogh…®va, egh a ban kogham. Kamagh…®ra, ia nan poroghan kogh, ia uaghan ban kogham. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® wain…®n ikarzim, ez…® ia wain…®n aghariba. Ez…® gumazim nan poroz…®, ez…® k…® an poro, a zurara bava ov…®zir av…®riba iti. Ez…® ia na ategh, ia bizir tam damighan kogham.  
\v 6 Eght…® gumazitam nan poroghan kogh, egh a mati wain…®n ikarzim…®n agharim me a makuniz…® a m…®s…®ngi. Egha me agharir kaba akuva da isava avim m…®k…®ra egha dagh aboi. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúIa nan porogh ik…®t…®, nan akam ian aven ikiam, eght…® ia uan ifongiam…®n bizitam bagh azangam, eght…® biziba ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n otivam.  
\v 8 Egh ia b…®va ov…®zir av…®riba ik…®, egh kamagh…®n ia nan suren gumazibar m…®n ikiam. Eght…® tuavir kam…®n nan Afeziam ziar ekiam iniam. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúAfeziam bar na gifonge, ez…® arazir kamra k…® ia gifonge. Egh ia nan poroght…® k…® ia gifuegh mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 10 K…® uan Afeziam…®n araziba ko akabar g…®n zui, egha an poroz…® a na gifongez…® mogh…®n, ia uaghan nan araziba ko akabar g…®n mang…®va egh nan poroght…® k…® ia gifuegh mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúNan navir agorogem ian ikiasa k…® ifonge. Ez…® agoroger kam bar ian navir averiabagh iz…®vagham. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ia m…®gei.  
\v 12 K…® ia m…®kemezir arazimra kara: k…® bar ia gifongez…® mogh…®n, arazir kamra ia uari uarigh ifongegh.  
\v 13 Gumazitam uan namakam a gifuegh egh a bagh aremegham, ez…® an arazir uarira uari ifongezim, a gumazamizir igharazibagh ifongezir araziba bar dagh afira.  
\v 14 Ez…® k…® ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ia ami, egha ia nan namakabar iti.  
\v 15 E fo, ingangarir gumazim bizir an gumazir ekiam amiba, a dagh fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® ua ‚Äòingangarir gumaziba‚Äô ia d…®borir puvat…®. Akaba bar k…® uan Afeziam da, da baregha egha k…® ia m…®kemegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ‚Äònamakaba‚Äô ia gar…®si. 
\p  
\v 16 ‚ÄúIa uari ko ikiasa na m…®sevezir pu. Puvat…®. Ia nan adarazir ikiasa k…® ia m…®sefe. Ez…® k…® ingangarim ia gan…®di, eght…® ia mang…®va egh b…®va dagher av…®riba ik…®, eght…® ian dagheba ik…®v…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n ia bizitam uari dan…®ngs…® nan ziam…®n Afeziam…®n azaraght…®, a ia dan…®ngam.  
\v 17 Kar nan arazim, k…® ia gan…®di: Ia uari uarigh ifongegh.‚Äù 
\s1 Nguazim…®n gumaziba suren gumazibar apanim damuam 
\p  
\v 18 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNguazim…®n gumaziba ian apanim damut…®, eght…® ia ok…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, me faragha uaghan nan apanim…®n ike.  
\v 19 Ez…® ia nguazir kam…®n gumazibar m…®n ikez…®, nguazim…®n gumaziba uan adarazigh ifongez…® mogh…®n, me ia gifueghai. Ez…® ia nguazir kam…®n gumaziba puvat…®. K…® ia m…®sevegha g…®fa, ez…® ia nguazir kam…®n araziba ategham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma nguazim…®n gumazamiziba ian aghuagha ian apanim gami.  
\v 20 Ia akar k…® ia m…®kemeziba deraghv…®ra da g…®n…®ghn…®gh, ingangarir gumazim uan gumazir ekiam gafirazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®ra me paza na gami, eght…® me uaghan paz…® ia damuam. Egh me na akam baragham, egh me uaghan ian akam baragham.  
\v 21 Egha me Afeziam g…®fozir puvat…®, a na amadaz…® k…® izes. Ez…® ia nan adarasi, kamagh…®n, me arazir kurar kaba bar dar ia damuam.  
\v 22 Ez…® k…® ti izeghan kogha egha akam me ganizir puvat…®z…®, me arazir kurabar os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®ghai. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me uan arazir kurabar mongan tuaviba puvat…®.  
\v 23 Ez…® gumazitam nan aghuagha nan apanim gami, a uaghan nan Afeziam…®n aghuagha an apanim gami.  
\v 24 K…® men tong…®n ikia mirakelbagh ami, da gumazir igharazi tam faragha amizir puvat…®zir ingangariba. Ez…® k…® men tong…®n mirakel…®n kabagh amizir puvat…®z…®, me arazir kurabar os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®ghai. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me mirakel…®n k…® amizibar ganigha g…®fa, egha me na ko Afeziam sara, gan aghuagha gan apanim gami.  
\v 25 Osizirir mam, Judan Arazibar aven iti, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumaziba pura nan apanim gami.‚Äô Ez…® akar kam guizbang…®ra otivasa, kamagh…®n me nan apanim gami. 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúGod…®n Duar Gavgavim ia Dan…®ngamim, a izam. An Afeziam ko iti, ez…® k…® ia bagh anemangam. A guizbang…®ra m…®geir Duam, egha an Afeziam ko ikegh izam. Egh a iz…®va derav…®ra nan araziba ko ingangaribar gun m…®k…®mam.  
\v 27 K…® faragh ingangarim gamima, ia na ko ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n. Kamagh…®n, ia uaghan nan gun m…®k…®mam. 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 ‚ÄúEz…® k…® kamagh sua, ia uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ataghraghan mark…®, kamagh…®n k…® bizir kam ia m…®keme.  
\v 2 Me ian anogoreght…® ia ua God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven ikian kogham. Eght…® g…®n dughiam otogham, gumaziba ia m…®sueght…® ia aremegham, egh me suam, me God…®n ingangarir aghuim gami.  
\v 3 Egha me Afeziam g…®fozir puvat…®, egha na g…®fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n me arazir kabar amuam.  
\v 4 K…® kamagh sua, gumaziba g…®n arazir kabar ia damut…®, eght…® ia akar k…® ia m…®kemezir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gham. Kamagh…®n, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir otivamin kaba, dar gun ia m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus God…®n Duam…®n ingangarim m…®gei. 
\p Egha Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® faragha uab…® ia ko iti, kamagh…®n k…® bizir kabar gun ia m…®kemezir puvat…®.  
\v 5 Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n Afeziar na amadaz…® ez…® k…® izezim, k…® a bagha zui. Ez…® ian tav nan azarazir puvat…®, ‚ÄòN…® managh zui?‚Äô  
\v 6 K…® akar kam ia m…®keme, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian naviba bar oseme.  
\v 7 Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, k…® ia ategha zui, kar ian akurvaghamim. K…® fo, k…® mang…®ghan koght…®, God…®n Duar Gavgavim ia Dan…®ngamim, a ia bagh izeghan kogham. Egh k…® mang…®gh…®va, k…® ia bagh anemadagham.  
\v 8 Eght…® a iz…®va nguazir kam…®n gumazibar amut…® me arazir kuram…®n m…®ngarim ko arazir aghuim…®n m…®ngarim ko God…®n kotiam…®n m…®ngarim, me dagh fogham  
\v 9 Arazir kuram…®n m…®ngarim, a kamak…®n, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim na itir puvat…®.  
\v 10 Arazir aghuim…®n m…®ngarim, a kamak…®n, k…® Afeziam bagh mang…®ght…®, ia ua nan ganighan kogham.\f + \ft (16:10) Nguazir kam…®n gumaziba Iesus isa kot gat…®gha ghaze, an arazir kuram gami, egh an ovengam. Ez…® God Iesus gamiz…® a ua d…®kaviz…® anenigha ghuz…®, an a ko iti. Arazir kamra, God gumazibar akagha ghaze, Iesus arazir aghuimram ami.\f* 
\v 11 God…®n kotiam…®n m…®ngarim, a kamak…®n, nguazir kam gativazir gumazir dapanim, God kotiam…®n aven a tuis…®gha g…®fa egha ghaze, a ivezir kuram inigh aremegham. 
\p  
\v 12 ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®k…®mamin akar av…®riba iti, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian n…®ghn…®ziba bar iz…®fa, eght…® ia bar da bareghan kogham.  
\v 13 Ez…® God…®n Duam, a guiz…®n akam m…®geir Duam, a iz…®va, ian n…®ghn…®zibar amut…® ia guiz…®n akaba bar dagh fogham. A uab…® uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n akatam m…®kemeghan kogham. Puvat…®. Akar an oraghizim, akar kamra an an gun m…®k…®mam. Egh a bizir g…®n otivamibar gun ia m…®k…®mam.  
\v 14 A nan akam inigh…®va egh an gun ia m…®k…®mam. Egh arazir kam…®n a nan ziar ekiam ko nan gavgavim, ian akagham.  
\v 15 Afeziam…®n biziba da bar nan biziba. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®keme, an Duam nan akam inigh…®va egh an gun ia m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\s1 Bar akongezir arazim, a navir os…®mt…®zim…®n danganim inigham 
\p  
\v 16 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar bar ovezim…®n ia ua nan ganighan kogham. Egh dughiar bar otevim…®n g…®n ia ua nan apigham.‚Äù  
\v 17 Ez…® suren gumazir maba uarira uarir tong…®n uariv gei, ‚ÄúKar akar manam…®n m…®ngarim an a gami? A ghaze, ‚ÄòDughiar bar ovezim…®n ia nan ganighan kogham. Egh ua dughiar otevim…®n g…®n ia ua nan apigham.‚Äô Egha uaghan ghaze, ‚ÄòBizir kam…®n m…®ngarim, a kamak…®n, k…® Afeziam bagha zui.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 18 Egha me m…®g…®a ghuav…®ra iti, ‚ÄúDughiar ovezir a m…®kemezir kam, a bizir tizim? E akar a m…®kemezir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus fo, me an azangs…®ghasa, ez…® a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ti tintinibar akar k…® m…®kemezir kam…®n m…®ngarim bagha azangs…®si? K…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòDughiar ovezim…®n ia nan ganighan kogham. Egh g…®n dughiar otevim…®n ia uan nan apigham.‚Äô Ia ti bizir kam bagha azai, o?  
\v 20 K…® bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia puv…®ram aziva arangam. Eght…® nguazim…®n gumazamiziba bar akuegham. Ian naviba osemegham. Eght…® ian navir os…®mt…®zir kam iraghr…®ght…®ma navir agorogem otogham.  
\v 21 Amizim borim batasava amuava, a fo, an m…®zazim iniamin dughiam otogha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n an oseme. Egha an otegha g…®vagha, a ua m…®zazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. An borim nguazim…®n otogha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…® a bar akonge.  
\v 22 Ez…® kamagh…®ra, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n naviba oseme. Eght…® k…® ua ian gant…®, ian naviba bar akuegham. Eght…® tav ian agoroger kam adeghan kogham.  
\v 23 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n ia ua bizitam bagh nan azaraghan kogham. K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia bizitam bagh nan ziam…®n Afeziam…®n azaraght…®ma eght…® a ia dan…®ngam.  
\v 24 Ia faragha bizitam nan ziam…®n azarazir puvat…®. Ia azangs…®gh…®va, egh ia iniam, eght…® agorogem bar ian navibagh iz…®vagham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus nguazir kam…®n gavgavim d…®kab…®raz…® a iraghu 
\p  
\v 25 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® akar is…®n zuim…®n akar kabar ia gami. K…® g…®n ua akar is…®n zuitam ia m…®kemeghan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® derav…®ra ia m…®k…®m…®va, egh Afeziam…®n ia m…®k…®mam.  
\v 26 Egh dughiar kam…®n ia nan ziam…®n azangs…®gham. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n m…®geir puvat…®, k…® ia bagh Afeziam…®n ko m…®k…®mam. Puvat…®.  
\v 27 Afeziam a uab…® ia gifonge. Ia a gifongegha ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikia egha fo, k…® Afeziam ko ikegha ize. Kamagh…®n a ia gifonge.  
\v 28 Guizbang…®ra, k…® fom…®ra Afeziam ko ikegha, egha k…® an ategha nguazim…®n ize. Egh dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® ua nguazim ategh, egh k…® ua Afeziam bagh mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® an suren gumaziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAre, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n derav…®ra m…®gei, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n akar is…®n zuibav geir puvat…®.  
\v 30 Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, n…® biziba bar dagh fo. Gumazitam bizir mam n…®n azangs…®ghasava amima, n…® an n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha g…®fa. N…® an azangs…®zim bagha m…®zuai puvat…®, n…® fogha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia ghaze, n…® God ko ikegha egha n…® ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúIa dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, o?  
\v 32 Ia oragh. Dughiam a rogh…®ra izi, egha a izegha g…®fa, eght…® me vaghvagh ian ag…®nt…®ght…® ia tintinibar uan nguibabar mangam. Egh ia na ateght…® k…® uab…®ra ikiam. Ez…® Afeziam na ko iti, kamagh…®n k…® bar uab…®ra ikeghan kogham.  
\v 33 Ia nan porogh…®v ik…®va egh ia navir am…®r…®zim ikiasa k…® ifonge. Kamagh sua k…® akar kam ia m…®keme. Eght…® ia nguazir kam…®n ik…®t…®, os…®mt…®ziba ia bativam. Egh ian naviba gavgavigh ik…®! K…® nguazir kam…®n gavgavim d…®kab…®ragha egha aneg…®fa!‚Äù 
\c 17  
\s1 Iesus suren gumaziba bagha God ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus suren gumazibav kemegha g…®vagha, egha kogha overiam…®n gara, egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfeziam, dughiam izegha g…®fa. Eght…® n…®n Otarim ziar ekiam n…® dan…®ngs…®, kamagh…®n n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ziar ekiam uan Otarim dan…®ngigh.  
\v 2 Kamagh…®n ami, n…® gavgavim a ganigha g…®fa. N…® kamagh…®n ifonge, a ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim gumazir n…® a gan…®ngiziba, bar me dan…®ngam. Kar zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim. Bizir kam bagha, n…® gumazamiziba bar men dapanim…®n ikiasa anem…®sefe.  
\v 3 Ez…® zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim, a kamak…®n: Gumazir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarir kam iniziba, me n…® g…®fo, n…® uab…®ra n…® guizbang…®n God. Egha me Krais Iesus g…®fo, n…® anemadaz…® a ize. 
\p  
\v 4 ‚ÄúK…® n…®n ziar ekiam ko gavgavim nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar akagha g…®fa. Egha k…®, ingangarir k…® damuasa n…® na gan…®ngizir kam, k…® a gamigha g…®fa.  
\v 5 Afeziam, fom…®ra nguazim t…®ghar otivam, k…® n…® ko ikia nan ziam ekefe. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® uan damazim…®n, n…® ua ziar ekiam na dan…®ngasa, k…® ifonge. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúK…® n…®n ziar ekiam isa nguazir kam…®n gumazir n…® na gan…®ngizibar aka. Me n…®n gumazamiziba, ez…® n…® me na ganigha g…®fa. Ez…® me derav…®ra n…®n akam baragha an g…®n zui.  
\v 7 Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, bizir n…® na gan…®ngiziba, da bar n…®rara ize.  
\v 8 Ez…® akar n…® na gan…®ngiziba, k…® bar da isa me gan…®ngi. Ez…® me da ini, egha me guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n fo, k…® fom…®ra n…® ko ikegha, egha k…® ize. Egha me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia kamagh…®n fo, n…® na amadaz…® ez…® k…® ize. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúK…® me bagha n…® ko m…®gei. K…® bar nguazim…®n gumazamiziba bagha n…® ko m…®geir pu. K…® fo, gumazamizir n…® na gan…®ngizir kaba, me n…®n adarasi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® me bagha n…® ko m…®gei.  
\v 10 Ez…® nan gumazamiziba, me n…®n adarasi. Ez…® n…®n gumazamiziba, me nan adarasi. Ez…® gumazamiziba nan gumazamizir kabar gari, me nan ziar ekiam g…®fo. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® bagh izam, egh k…® ua nguazim…®n ikian kogham. Ez…® me nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® Afeziam, n…® bar zue ez…® tav n…®n m…®n itir puvat…®! K…® kamagh sua, me uari inigh navir vam…®ra ik…®, mati n…® na ko, ga uaning inigha iti mogh…®n. Bizir kam bagha, n…® uan ziam…®n gavgavim…®n derav…®ra men gan. Kar ziar n…® na gan…®ngizim.  
\v 12 Ez…® dughiar k…® me ko itiba, k…® n…®n ziam…®n gavgavim…®n men gari. Kar ziar n…® na gan…®ngizim. K…® bar derav…®ra men garima men tav ovengezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazir ovengamim, a uab…®ram ovengam. K…® kamagh sua, n…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akam guizbang…®ra otivam, kamagh…®n gumazir kam ovengam. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® bagha izi. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, nan agorogem men navibagh iz…®vagh ikiam. Kamagh…®n, dughiar k…® nguazim…®n itim, k…® akar kabav m…®keme. 
\p  
\v 14 ‚ÄúN…®n akam, k…® me ganigha g…®fa. K…® nguazir kam…®n gumazim puvat…®. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, nan gumazamiziba me nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba men aghuagha men apanim gami.  
\v 15 K…®, n…® nguazir kam…®n me inigh azenan mangasa n…®n azangs…®zir pu. Puvat…®. K…®, n…® men ganasa, k…® n…®n azai, eght…® Gumazir Kuram paz…® me damuan kogham.  
\v 16 K…® uab…® k…® nguazir kam…®n gumazim puvat…®. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, me nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®.  
\v 17 Ez…® n…®n akam a bar guizbang…®ra. Ez…® k…®, n…® uan akam damut…® a men navir averiabar ingarasa, k…® ifonge. Eght…® n…® me damut…® me uari is…® n…® dan…®ngam  
\v 18 N…® fom…®ra na amadaz…® ez…® k…® izegha nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n iti. Ez…® kamagh…®ra n…® gumazir na gan…®ngiziba, k…® me amadagha ghaze, me nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikiam.  
\v 19 K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, me bar guizbang…®ra uari is…® n…® dan…®ngam. Bizir kam bagha k…® men akurvaghasa, k…® bar uab…® isa n…® gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄúK…® gumazir kabara bagha God ko m…®geir puvat…®. K…®, gumazamizir men akam baragh egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikiamiba, k…® uaghan me bagha God ko m…®gei.  
\v 21 Egha gumazir kaba bar navir vam…®ra ikiasa k…® ifonge. Afeziam, n…® nan aven itima k…® n…®n aven iti, ez…® kamagh…®ra me gan aven ikiasa k…® ifonge. Eght…® nguazim…®n gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® egh fogh suam, n…® na amadaz…® ez…® k…® ize. Kamagh…®n k…® ghaze, me bar navir vam…®ra ik…®.  
\v 22 K…® ghaze, n…® na ko, ga navir vam…®ra iti mogh…®n, kamagh…®ra me navir vam…®ra ikiam. Bizir kam bagha, n…® ziar ekiar na gan…®ngizim, k…® ziar ekiar kamra isa me gan…®ngi.  
\v 23 K…® kamagh sua, nguazim…®n gumazamiziba fogh suam, n…® na amadaz…® ez…® k…® ize. Egh fogh suam, n…® na gifongez…® mogh…®ra n…® nan adarazigh ifonge. Kamagh…®n k…® men aven iti, ez…® n…® nan aven iti, ez…® arazir kam…®n me guizbang…®ra navir vam…®ra ikiasa k…® ifonge. 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄúAfeziam, gumazamizir n…® na gan…®ngiziba, me na ko nguibar k…® itim…®n ikiasa k…® ifonge. Me nan angazangarir ekiam ko nan gavgavim…®n ganasa k…® ifonge. Dughiar nguazim t…®ghar otivam, n…® na gifonge, egha n…® angazangarir kam ko gavgavim na gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 25 ‚ÄúN…® Arazir Aghuibara Amir Afeziam, nguazim…®n gumazamiziba n…® g…®fozir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® n…® g…®fo. Ez…® nan adarasi, me fo, n…® na amadaz…® ez…® k…® ize.  
\v 26 K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, me igharazigh ifongezir arazim inigham, n…® na gifongez…® mogh…®n. Eght…® k…® uaghan men aven ikiam. Kamagh…®n k…® n…® isa men aka, egh k…® kamagh…®n damu mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 18  
\ms1 Iesus m…®zazim inigha aremegha egha ua d…®kafi 
\mr (Sapta 18-20) 
\s1 Judas Iesus isa apanibar agharim gat…® 
\r (Matyu 26:47-56 ko Mak 14:43-50 ko Luk 22:47-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n God ko m…®kemegha g…®vagha, egha uan suren gumaziba ko me ghua Kidron…®n zarim gir…®gha vong…®n ghu. Ez…® d…®par kam…®n vong…®n azenir mam iti, ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko me azenir kam…®n aven ghue.  
\v 2 Dughiar av…®ribar Iesus uan suren gumaziba azenir kam…®n me batifi. Kamagh…®n Judas, a Iesus is…® gumazir apanibar agharim dar…®ghamim, a uaghan azenir kam g…®fo.  
\v 3 Egha Judas, a Rom…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Farisiba amadazir plis…®n maba, a me inigha danganir kam…®n ghue. Egha me adenir aviba ko lamba ko m…®dorozir biziba sara suigha zui.  
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus bizir a bativamiba a bar dagh fo. Egha a s…®vagha men borogh…®ra ghua egha kamagh…®n me azai, ‚ÄúIa tina buri?‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® me kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúE Nasaret…®n gumazim Iesus buriasa izi.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar k…®rara.‚Äù Dughiar kam Judas, a gumazir Iesus isa me gan…®dim, a me ko tughav iti.  
\v 6 Me Iesus barazi a m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar k…®rara,‚Äù egha me ua s…®vagha ghua nguazim gire.  
\v 7 Ez…® Iesus ua men azara, ‚ÄúIa tina buri?‚Äù Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúNasaret…®n gumazim Iesus.‚Äù  
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®kemegha g…®fa, kar k…®rara. Kamagh…®n ia na buriva, gumazir kaba ateght…® me mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 9 A kamagh sua an akar fom…®ra m…®kemezim, an daghem otogham, ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir n…® na gan…®ngiziba, men tav ovengezir puvat…®.‚Äù Kamagh…®n an arazir kam gami. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Saimon Pita m…®dorozir sabar mam inigha ize, egha uan sabam a m…®k…®r…®gha egha ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim…®n ingangarir gumazim m…®suegha, egha an kuarir guvim…®n itim atu, ez…® a ir…®. Ingangarir gumazir kam…®n ziam, Malkus.  
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® sabam inigh ua an nodozim darugh. Manmagh ami? N…® ghaze, k…® ti Afeziam na gan…®ngizir os…®mt…®zir kam inian kogham, o?‚Äù 
\s1 Me Iesus inigha Anas bagha zui 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Rom…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko men gumazir ekiam, ko Judan plis…®n gumaziba, me Iesus…®n suighava egha benim…®n a ike.  
\v 13 Egha faraghava a inigha Anas bagha ghu. Anas a Kaiafas…®n ivozir afeziam. Kaiafas a azenir kam…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim.  
\v 14 Egha Kaiafas, Judaba kamagh…®n me m…®kemezir gumazim, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n a dera, gumazir vam…®ra gumazamizibar danganim inigh egh aremegham.‚Äù 
\s1 Pita ghaze, a Iesus g…®fozir puvat…® 
\r (Matyu 26:69-70 ko Mak 14:66-68 ko Luk 22:55-57) 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Saimon Pita ko suren gumazir igharazir mam, aning Iesus…®n g…®n zui. Ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim, a suren gumazir kam g…®fo, ez…® kamagh…®n a Iesus…®n g…®n ghua ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim…®n d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven ghu.  
\v 16 Ez…® Pita azenan ikia tiar akam…®n borogh…®ra tughav iti. Ez…® suren gumazir igharazim, a ghua amizir tiar akam…®n garim m…®kemegha, egha Pita inigha aven zui.  
\v 17 Ez…® amizir tiar akam…®n garim a kamagh…®n Pitan azara, ‚ÄúN…® ti uaghan gumazir kam…®n suren gumazim?‚Äù Ez…® Pita ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. K…® an suren gumazim pu.‚Äù  
\v 18 Ez…® danganim bar orangi. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ingangarir gumaziba ko plis…®n gumaziba me avir mam at…®. Egha me avim…®n f…®ava an m…®n tuivighav iti. Ez…® Pita uaghan me ko tughav ikia egha avim…®n f…®a iti. 
\s1 Ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim Iesus…®n kotim gami 
\r (Matyu 26:59-66 ko Mak 14:55-64 ko Luk 22:66-71) 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim, a Iesus…®n suren gumaziba ko akar a men sure gamizim bagha, a Iesus…®n azangs…®si.  
\v 20 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® gumazamiziba azenara me m…®keme. Egha k…® zurara God ko m…®geir d…®peniba ko God…®n D…®penim…®n aven gumazamizibar sure gami. Kar danganir Judaba bar uari akuviba. K…® modogha akatam m…®kemezir pu.  
\v 21 Ez…® manmagh amiz…® n…® nan azangs…®si? N…® gumazir akar kam baraghizibar azangs…®gh. Me k…® m…®kemezir akam g…®fo.‚Äù  
\v 22 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®geima ez…® plis…®n gumazir mam tughav ikia, egha an an guam a m…®suegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim…®n akam ikara, kar ti arazir aghuim, o?‚Äù  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® akar kuratam m…®kemeght…®, eght…® n…® derav…®ra akar k…® m…®kemezim an gun m…®k…®m. Eght…® k…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuim damight…®, ez…® n…® tizim bagha na apese?‚Äù  
\v 24 Ez…® Anas Iesus isa ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim Kaiafas bagha anemada. Egha me Iesus ikezir benim f…®rizir puvat…®. 
\s1 Pita ua ghaze, a Iesus g…®fozir puvat…® 
\r (Matyu 26:71-75 ko Mak 14:69-72 ko Luk 22:58-62) 
\p  
\v 25 Saimon Pita tughav ikia egha avim…®n f…®i. Ez…® me kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® ti uaghan an suren gumazir mam?‚Äù Ez…® a m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. K…® an suren gumazim puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dapanim…®n ingangarir gumazir mam iti, a Pita kuarim atuzir gumazim…®n adarazir mav. A ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ti n…®n gani, n…® Iesus ko azenim…®n aven ikes?‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® Pita ua m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® dughiar kamra tuarim ake. 
\s1 Me Iesus inigha Pailat bagha zui 
\r (Matyu 27:1-2 ko 27:11-14 ko Mak 15:1-5 ko Luk 23:1-5) 
\p  
\v 28 Egha Judaba Iesus inigha Kaiafas…®n d…®penim ategha an akua gavman…®n dapanir ekiam…®n d…®penim…®n zui. Ka bar m…®zaraghara. Egha me ghaze, ‚ÄúE God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegh…®va, egh e God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isar ekiam…®n as…®zim rameghan kogham.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me uari gavman dapanir ekiam…®n d…®penim…®n aven ghuzir puvat…®.\f + \ft (18:28) Gavman…®n faragha zuir gumaziba, Pailat ko an adarasi, me bar Rom…®n gumaziba. Egha Judabar Arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Me God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ikiamin n…®ghn…®ziba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Judaba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, me Rom…®n gumaziba ko porogh…®va God…®n damazim…®n ti m…®zegham.\f* 
\v 29 Me azenan iti, ez…® Pailat me bagha izi, egha kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa akar manam gumazir kam gasaraz…®, a kot…®n iti?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® me kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúAn arazir kuram gamir puvat…®z…®, e n…® bagha a inigha izeghan koghai.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® Pailat kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n, ia a inigh mang…®va uan Arazibagh is…®n a tuis…®gh.‚Äù Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúE gumazir tam puram a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan kogham.‚Äù\f + \ft (18:31) Rom…®n gavman Judabar Nguazim gatifa. Egha me amamangat…®z…®, Judaba uari uan kot…®n aven bizitabar ak…®ram. Egha me Judabar kotiabar kamagh…®n anogoroke, me gumazitam bagh m…®k…®mt…®, an aremeghan markiam. Arazir gumazim ter ighuvim gafuz…® an aremeghamim, kar Rombar arazimra.\f* 
\v 32 (Iesus fom…®ra uan ovengamin arazim m…®gei. A kamagh sua, an akar kam guizbang…®ra otivam, ez…® kamagh…®n Pailat ko Judaba kamagh…®n uariv gei, ez…® bizir kam oto.) 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® Pailat uamategha gavman…®n d…®penim…®n aven ghua, egha Iesus…®n diaz…®ma a izi. Ez…® a kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® Judabar Atrivim, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúN…® uab…® n…®ghn…®gha egha n…® akar kam gami, o gumazir igharazitam nan gun n…® m…®keme?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Ez…® Pailat kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? N…® ghaze, k…® Judan mav, o? N…® uan adarazi ko ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, me n…®n akua na bagha ize. N…® bizir tizim gami?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúK…® nguazir kam…®n atrivim puvat…®. K…® nguazir kam…®n atrivim…®n ikiai, kamagh…®n nan ingangarir gumaziba na bagha m…®soghai, egha tav na isa Judabar agharim gat…®ghan koghai. Ez…® k…® nguazir kam…®n atrivibar m…®n ingarir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…® Pailat an azara, ‚ÄúEz…® n…® guizbang…®ra atrivir mam, o?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúAtrivim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam, kar n…®n akamra. Amebam na batez…® ez…® k…® nguazir kam…®n ingangarir vam…®ra damuasa ize. Ingangarir kam kamak…®n: k…® guiz…®n akam akunam. Egha gumazir guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n mangamiba, me nan akam barasi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® Pailat an azara, ‚ÄúGuiz…®n akam, a bar bizir tizimra?‚Äù 
\s1 Pailat ter ighuvim…®n Iesus gafughasa m…®gei 
\r (Matyu 27:15-31 ko Mak 15:6-20 ko Luk 23:13-25) 
\p Pailat m…®kemegha g…®vagha egha ua Judaba bagha azenan ghu. Egha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® an arazir kuratam batozir puvat…®.  
\v 39 Egha ia, arazir k…® g…®n zuir kam, ia a g…®fo. Ez…® azeniba bar, God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n, k…® ian arazim…®n g…®n ghua gumazir vam…®ra kalabus…®n a isa azenim gat…®. Ia ifueght…® k…® Judabar atrivir kam f…®righ ia bagh anemangam, o?‚Äù  
\v 40 Ez…® me kamagh…®n d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMam puvat…®! N…® Barabasra a f…®righ!‚Äù (Barabas, a gumazir okeim egha uaghan m…®sosi.)\f + \ft (18:40) Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Barabas, a gumazir Judan nguazim bagha Rom…®n gavman ko m…®sozir mav.\f* 
\c 19  
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Pailat me m…®kemez…® me Iesus inigha a ifozorosi.  
\v 2 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®koniba itir beniba inigha egha atrivim…®n dapanir asuam…®n m…®n an ingarigha, an dapanim garu. Egha me korotiar aghevir mam a garu.  
\v 3 Egha me an borogh…®ra izegha a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJudabar Atrivim, n…®rara atrivir ekiam!‚Äù Egha me kamagh…®n m…®g…®ava an guam apezav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Pailat ua azenan ghugha kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh. K…® a inigh ia bagh azenan izam, eght…® ia fogham, k…® an arazir kuratam…®n apizir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus azenan zui. Ez…® dapanir asuar me benir d…®koniba itim…®n ingarizim, an an dapanim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® korotiar aghevir kam, a uaghan an ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® Pailat me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gan, gumazir kam a kara.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko plis…®n gumaziba an ganigha kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúTer ighuvim…®n a gafugh! Ter ighuvim…®n a gafugh!‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Pailat kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari a inigh…®va egh ter ighuvim…®n a gafugh. K…® uab…®, k…® an arazir kuratam…®n apizir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúA uab…® ghaze ‚ÄòK…® God…®n Otarim.‚Äô Ez…® en Arazibar Osizirir mam iti, ez…® arazir kam kamagh…®n m…®gei, gumazir kamagh m…®geim, an aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Pailat akar kam baregha egha bar atiatingi.  
\v 9 Egha a ua ghua gavman…®n d…®penim…®n aven ghugha, egha kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azai, ‚ÄúN…® nguibar manam…®n ikegha ize?‚Äù Ez…® Iesus an akar kam ikarazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Pailat a m…®gei, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…® n…® nan akam ikarvaghan aghua? K…® n…® f…®righamin gavgavim iti, egha uaghan n…® is…®v temer ighuvim gafughamin gavgavim iti. Ez…® n…® ti bizir kam g…®fozir puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúGod…®n p…®n itim, a gavgavim n…® gan…®ngizir puvat…®ghai, n…® na d…®kab…®namin gavgaviba puvat…®gham. Ez…® gumazir na isa n…®n agharim gat…®zim, an arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim, a n…®n arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim, bar a gafira.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Pailat akar kam baregha egha Iesus ateght…® a mangasa tuaviba buri. Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúN…® gumazir kam ateght…® a mang…®t…®, n…® Sisar…®n namakam puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, gumazim uab…®ra uab…® m…®g…®a ghaze, an atrivim, egha a Sisar…®n apanim.‚Äù  
\v 13 Pailat akar kam baregha, egha Iesus…®n akua azenan ghu. Egha a jas…®n dabirabim gaperaghav iti, danganir kam me ‚ÄúDag…®ar Azuarim‚Äù a gar…®si. (Hibrun akam me ghaze, ‚ÄúGabata‚Äù). 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® dughiar kam a dughiar me God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isam bagha daghebar amuva bizibar k…®ram. Kar aruer ar…®zim. Ez…® Pailat Judabav gei, ‚ÄúIa ganigh! Ian Atrivim kara.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Egha me kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúA batokegh! A batueght…® a mang…®! Ter ighuvim…®n a gafugh!‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Pailat men azara, ‚ÄúIa ifonge, k…® ian Atrivim is…® ter ighuvim…®n a gafugham?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba kamagh…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúE atrivir igharaziba puvat…®. Sisar bar uab…®ra!‚Äù  
\v 16 Kamagh…®n amiz…® Pailat Iesus inigha, me ter ighuvim…®n a gafughasa, a men agharim gat…®. 
\s1 Me Iesus isa ter ighuvim…®n a gafu 
\r (Matyu 27:32-44 ko Mak 15:21-32 ko Luk 23:26-43) 
\p Ez…® me Iesus inigha zui.  
\v 17 Ez…® a uab…® uan ter ighuvim gupugha, egha nguibar ekiam ategha egha danganir mam…®n zui, an ziam ‚ÄúDapanir Agharir Danganim.‚Äù (Ez…® Hibrun akam me ghaze ‚ÄúGolgota.‚Äù)  
\v 18 Ez…® danganir kam…®n me a isa ter ighuvim…®n anegura. Egha me gumazir igharazir pumuning a ko, aning agura, mam vong…®n itima, mam vong…®n iti. Ez…® Iesus aning…®n torim…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Pailat uaghan me m…®geima me ziar mam osirigha ter ighuvim gat…®. Ziar kam a kamak…®n, ‚ÄúNasaret…®n Gumazim Iesus, Judabar Atrivim.‚Äù  
\v 20 Me ziar kam, Hibrun akam ko Rom…®n akam ko Grigh…®n akam…®n, men akabar an osiri. Danganir me Iesus ter ighuvim…®n anegurazim, a nguibar ekiam borogh…®ra iti, kamagh…®n amiz…® Judan av…®rim izava osizirir kam…®n gara egha a d…®bori. 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba kamagh…®n Pailat m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n osiran mark…®, ‚ÄòJudan Atrivim.‚Äô Bar mark…®. N…® ziam kamagh…®n an osirigh, ‚ÄòGumazir kam ghaze, k…® Judabar Atrivim.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Pailat men akam ikara, ‚ÄúMark…®. Akar k…® osirigha g…®vazim, a kamagh…®ra ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 M…®dorozir gumaziba ter ighuvim…®n Iesus gafugha g…®vagha, egha g…®n me an korotiaba inigha egha 4 plan akuabar uari rome. Egha me akuar vam…®ra vam…®ra isi. Egha me uaghan an korotiar ruarim sara ini, egha m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n gari, me inir akuar av…®riba inigha korotiar ruarir kam isamizir pu. Puvat…®. Me inir vamiram an ingari, egha me a isamizir puvat…®.  
\v 24 Egha m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúE korotiar ruarir kam abighan kogham. Puvat…®. E satu gikararang…®va gumazir a iniamim g…®fogham.‚Äù 
\p God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akar mam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe nan korotiaba tuiragh, egh uari dan…®ngam. Egh me satu gikararang…®va gumazim am…®seveght…® a nan korotiar ruarim iniam.‚Äù Ez…® akar kam guizbang…®ra otoghasa, kamagh…®n arazir kamra m…®dorozir gumaziba a gami. 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus…®n amebam ko, an amebam…®n afumim ko, Klopas…®n amuim Maria ko, Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim Maria, me bar an ter ighuvim…®n borogh…®ra tuivighav iti  
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus garima an amebam ko suren gumazir a bar ifongezim, aning rogh…®ra tughav iti. Ez…® a kamagh…®n uan amebam m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmizim, gumazir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n, a n…®n otarim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® a kamagh…®n suren gumazir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmizir kam, a dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n amebam.‚Äù Ez…® dughiar kam…®n ghua, suren gumazir kam Maria inigha uan d…®penim…®n ghugha egha an gara uan amebam…®n m…®n a gami. 
\s1 Iesus areme 
\r (Matyu 27:45-56 ko Mak 15:33-41 ko Luk 23:44-49) 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus fo, an ingangariba dat…®r…®gh…®n bar g…®fa. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan kuarim nan p…®ri.‚Äù God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akar mam guizbang…®ra otivasa, kamagh…®n an akar kam gami.  
\v 29 Ez…® m…®ner mam wain…®n afangt…®zim an ikia rogh…®ra iti. Egha me d…®pam…®n suizir bizim inigha egha wain…®n d…®pam garu. Ez…® wain a giz…®vaz…®ma, me a isa hisop…®n aghorim gikegha a isa Iesus…®n akam dar…®ghasa an amadi.  
\v 30 Ez…® Iesus wain…®n kam amegha g…®vagha, egha m…®gei, ‚ÄúA dat…®r…®gh…®n g…®fa.‚Äù Egha a dapanim aviragha egha uan duam sue. 
\s1 M…®dorozir gumazir mam Iesus…®n ivim b…®ra 
\p  
\v 31 Kar dughiar me Sabat bagha bizibar ak…®rim. Sabat…®n dughiar kam, a dughiar bar ekiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Judaba me gumazir kuaba dughiar kam temer ighuvibar ikian me aghua. Egha me Pailat kamagh…®n an azangs…®gha ghaze, a men amamangat…®ght…® me temer ighuvibar itir gumazibar suer agharibav sogh da ap…®right…®, me zuam…®ram aremeght…® me men kuaba adegh izighram.  
\v 32 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua gumazir Iesus ko guraghav itir mam…®n suer agharimning m…®sogha aning ap…®righa, egha ghua gumazir igharazim uaghan an suer agharimning m…®sogha aning ap…®ri.  
\v 33 Egha me iza Iesus…®n garima an aremegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me an suer agharimning ap…®rizir puvat…®.  
\v 34 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir mam afuzim inigha Iesus…®n ivim b…®ra. Ez…® ghuzim ko d…®pam zuam…®ra ire.  
\v 35 (K…®, Jon, k…® gumazir bizir kam…®n ganizim, k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ia bizir kam g…®fogh…®va n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam. Kamagh…®n k…® an gun ia m…®gei. Akar k…® gun m…®geir kam, a guizbang…®ra. K…® uab…® fo, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei.)  
\v 36 God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akar mam, a kamak…®n, ‚ÄúMe an agharitam ap…®righan kogham.‚Äù God kamagh sua, akar kam guizbang…®ram otogham, ez…® kamagh…®n bizir kam oto.  
\v 37 Ez…® akar igharazir mam God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n iti, a kamak…®n, ‚ÄúMe, gumazir afuzim…®n ruazir kam bagh ganam.‚Äù 
\s1 Me Iesus…®n kuam isa mozir igiar mam gat…® 
\r (Matyu 27:57-61 ko Mak 15:42-47 ko Luk 23:50-56) 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® g…®n Arimatean nguibam…®n gumazim Josep ghua Iesus…®n kuam iniasa Pailat…®n azangs…®si. Josep a Iesus…®n suren gumazir mam, egha a Judabar atiatigha, egha uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim modo. Ez…® Pailat an amamangat…®z…®, a ghuava Iesus…®n kuam ini.  
\v 39 Ez…® Nikodemus, gumazir faragha d…®magarim…®n Iesus…®n ganizim, a uaghan ize. Egha borer mughuriar aghuir maba inigha ize, me temer pumuning…®n borem inigha aning veregha, egha borer kam gami. Ez…® borer kam…®n os…®mt…®zim 30 plan kilogram…®n ghu.  
\v 40 Ez…® Josep ko Nikodemus aning Iesus…®n kuam inigha borer kam an kuam gaghui. Egha inir aghuim…®n an m…®karzim nomke, Judaba uan gumazir oveaghuezibagh ami mogh…®n.  
\v 41 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus ter ighuvim…®n anegurazir danganir kam…®n borogh…®ra, azenir mam iti. Egha azenir kam…®n mozir igiar mam iti, me dag…®ar torim atugha, egha me faragha gumazitam…®n kuatam a gat…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 42 Kar dughiar Judaba Sabat…®n dughiam bagh bizibar k…®ramim, ez…® mozir kam, a Iesus aremezir danganim borogh…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning Iesus…®n kuam inigha ghua mozir kam…®n anet…®. 
\c 20  
\s1 Iesus ua d…®kafi 
\r (Matyu 28:1-8 ko Mak 16:1-8 ko Luk 24:1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Sanden bar m…®zaraghara, am…®nim m…®tateghav…®ra iti, ez…® Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim Maria, a mozim…®n ghu. Egha a garima mozim…®n tiar akam gasarazir dag…®am ua itir puvat…®.\f + \ft (20:1) Wikbar faraghav…®ra zuir aruem, a Sandera.\f* 
\v 2 Ez…® a, Saimon Pita ko suren gumazir igharazir kam, a gumazir Iesus bar ifongezim, an aning bagha ivegha ghu. Egha Maria kamagh…®n aning…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe Ekiam…®n kuam mozim…®n a inigha ghu, ez…® e fozir puvat…®, me managh anet…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Pita ko suren gumazir igharazir kam, aning nguibam ategha egha mozim…®n zui.  
\v 4 Aning v…®rara ivegha ghua, suren gumazir igharazir kam Pita gafiragha, egha faragha mozim…®n oto.  
\v 5 Egha an aviragha mozim…®n aven gari, egha inir aghuir me Iesus…®n kuam avarazir kabar gara egha an aven ghuzir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Saimon Pita an g…®n ghua, mozim…®n averiam…®n ghu. Egha a inir aghuir kabar garima da iti.  
\v 7 Egha a inir igharazir mam…®n garima a uaghan iti, a inir me Iesus…®n dapanim…®n ikezim. Inir kam a inir igharaziba ko itir puvat…®. Saimon ghaze, me ti a righa egha igharagha anet…®.  
\v 8 Ez…® suren gumazir igharazir faragha mozim…®n otozim, a uaghan aven ghu. Egha a bizir kabar ganigha egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti.  
\v 9 (Guizbang…®ra, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akam ghaze, Iesus mozim…®n ua d…®kavigham. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n aning akar kam t…®ghar deraghv…®ra a g…®fogham.)  
\v 10 Egha suren gumazimning uamategha d…®penim…®n ghu. 
\s1 Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim Maria Iesus…®n gani 
\r (Matyu 28:9-10 ko Mak 16:9-11) 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Maria mozim…®n azenan tughav ikia azi. Egha an aziav…®ra ikia egha aviragha mozim…®n averiam…®n gari.  
\v 12 Egha a ensel…®n pumuning…®n garima, aning korotiar ghurghurimning aru. Egha aning danganir Iesus…®n kuam faragha ikezim…®n aperaghav iti. Egha mam an dapanim ikezir nagh…®n apera ez…® mam an suemning ikezir nagh…®n apera.  
\v 13 Egha aning kamagh…®n Marian azai, ‚ÄúAmizim, n…® manmagh suava azi?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® a kamagh…®n aning…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe nan Ekiam…®n kuam inigha ghu, ez…® k…® fozir puvat…®, me managh anet…®.‚Äù  
\v 14 A kamagh…®n m…®g…®ava, ragha garima, Iesus tughav iti. Ez…® Maria fozir puvat…®, ka Iesus.  
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúAmizim, n…® manmagh suava azi? N…® tina buri?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Maria ghaze, kar ti azenim…®n garir gumazim, egha a kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir aruam, n…® an kuam inigha ghu, egh danganir n…® an at…®zim…®n gun na m…®kemegh. Eght…® k…® mang…®va a iniam.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúMaria!‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Maria ragha kamagh…®n Hibrun akam…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúRabonai.‚Äù Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim a kamak…®n, ‚ÄúTisa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® t…®ghar uan Afeziam bagh mavanangam, kamagh…®n n…® nan suiraghv…®ra ikian mark…®. Egh n…® nan aveghbuaba bagh mang…®va egh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, kon Afeziam, ko men Afeziam, k…® a bagha uamategha ghuavanadi. A nan God, ko uaghan men God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Makdalan Maria ghua suren gumaziba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Ekiam…®n ganigha g…®fa.‚Äù Egha an akar Iesus a m…®kemezim…®n gun me m…®gei. 
\s1 Suren gumaziba Iesus…®n gani 
\r (Matyu 28:16-20 ko Mak 16:14-18 ko Luk 24:36-49) 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Sanden guarat…®zim…®n am…®nim p…®righa g…®fa. Ez…® suren gumaziba me Judabar atiatingi, egha d…®penir me itim, me pamten an tiar akaba ase, eght…® azenan itir gumazitam aven izan kogham. Ez…® Iesus iza pura suren gumazibar tong…®n tughav iti. Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan naviba am…®ragh ik…®.‚Äù  
\v 20 A kamagh…®n m…®g…®a, uan duar torir dafarimning…®n itimning ko duar ivir vuem…®n itim, men aka. Ez…® suren gumaziba Ekiam…®n ganigha me bar akonge.  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus ua me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan naviba am…®ragh ik…®. Afeziam na amadaz…® ez…® k…® ize. Ez…® kamagh…®ra k…® ia amadima ia zui.‚Äù  
\v 22 A kamagh…®n m…®g…®a, egha uan am…®nim men a giveragha men amada, egha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa God…®n Duam uan navir averiabar a inigh.  
\v 23 Egh ia gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham, eght…® God uaghan men arazir kuraba g…®n amadaght…®, da ua puvat…®gham. Eght…® ia men arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan koght…®, men arazir kuraba ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Tomas Iesus…®n gani 
\p  
\v 24 Dughiar Iesus uan suren gumaziba batozim, men 12 plan suren gumazibar mav, a me ko itir puvat…®. Kar Tomas, an ziar mam Fufuzim.  
\v 25 Ez…® suren gumazir igharaziba kamagh…®n Tomas m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Ekiam…®n ganigha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Tomas kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® an duar torir me an dafarimning gafuziming…®n ganighan kogh…®va, egh k…® uan dafarpuzim an duar torimning dat…®ghan kogh…®va, egh k…® uan dafarim an ivir vuem…®n itir duam dat…®ghan kogh…®va, egh k…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikian kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® 7 plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®ma, suren gumaziba ua d…®penim…®n aven iti, ez…® Tomas me ko aven iti. Me tiar akaba bar pamten da asegha g…®fa. Ez…® Iesus iza men tong…®n tughav iti. Egha me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan naviba am…®ragh ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Egha a kamagh…®n Tomas m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarpuzim…®n kagh suiragh, egh n…® nan dafarimning…®n ganigh. Egh n…® uan agharim amadagh uan dafarim nan ivir vuem…®n itir duam dat…®gh. N…® n…®ghn…®zir pumuning ikian mark…®. N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Tomas kamagh…®n an akam ikara, ‚ÄúN…® nan Ekiam. N…® nan God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan ganigha g…®fa, egha n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan iti, o? Gumazir na ganizir puvat…®ziba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®va, egh gumazir kaba bar akuegham.‚Äù 
\s1 Ak…®nafarir kam…®n m…®ngarim 
\p  
\v 30 Iesus mirakel…®n av…®rir maba uaghan suren gumazibar damazim…®n dagh ami. Ez…® k…® bar Ak…®nafarir kam…®n da osirizir puvat…®.  
\v 31 Egha, akar k…® osirizir kam, k…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikiasa, k…® an osiri. A Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim, a God…®n Otarim. Eght…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®va, egh ia an ziam…®n zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. K…® kamagh sua, ak…®nafarir kam an osiri. 
\c 21  
\ms1 Iesus ua uab…® isa uan suren gumazibar aka 
\mr (Sapta 21) 
\s1 7 plan suren gumaziba Iesus…®n gani 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma Iesus ua uan suren gumaziba Galilin d…®pam…®n borogh…®ra uab…® isa men aka. Galilin d…®pam…®n ziar mam Taiberias…®n d…®pam. Bizir kam kamagh…®n oto.  
\v 2 Dughiar kam Saimon Pita ko Tomas (an ziar mam Fufuzim), ko Nataniel (an nguibam, Kanan nguibar Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itim), ko Sebedin otarir pumuning, ko Iesus…®n suren gumazir igharazir pumuning, me bar uari inigha iti.  
\v 3 Egha Saimon Pita kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® osiriba buris…® mangam.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúE n…® ko mangam.‚Äù Egha me d…®kavigha bot…®n mam…®n ghuavanabogha egha me zui. Ez…® d…®magarir kam…®n me osirir taba inizir puvat…®.  
\v 4 Ez…® aruem anangasa ov…®rima, me gumazir mam…®n garima a d…®pam…®n dadarim…®n tughav iti. Ez…® suren gumaziba kamagh…®n fozir pu, kar Iesus.  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúOtariba, ia osiritaba iniz, o?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® me kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ivem inigh, agharir guvir bot…®n amadaghan itim…®n anekunigh, egh ia osiritaba inigham.‚Äù Kamagh…®n me ivem akuniz…® a iraghu, ez…® me osirir bar av…®riba inigha, egha ua ivem gekuigha anagav avenge.  
\v 7 Ez…® suren gumazir Iesus bar ifongezim, a kamagh…®n Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar Ekiamra.‚Äù Pita faragha ingarasava uan korotiar aruzim sue. Egha a kamagh…®n oraki, ‚ÄúKar Ekiamra,‚Äù egha korotiam uam anerugha uab…® ikegha egha d…®pam uab…® akunigha egha d…®pam…®n ghua dadarim…®n oto.  
\v 8 Ez…® suren gumazir igharaziba me bot…®n zui, egha me ivem osiriba sara anem…®k…®r…®gha zui. Me d…®par dadarim…®n borogh…®n 100 mitan m…®n iti.  
\v 9 Ez…® me iza dadarim…®n otogha g…®vagha, egha me avir mam…®n garima osiri maba avim gis…®n iti. Ez…® bret…®n maba sara iti. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúOsirir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n iniziba, ia taba inigh iz…®.‚Äù  
\v 11 Ez…® Saimon Pita bot…®n ghuavanabogha egha ivem a m…®k…®r…®gha d…®par dadarim…®n ghu. Ez…® osirir ekiabara ivem giz…®fa, da bar mogh…®ra, 153 plan osiriba. Egha osiriba bar av…®raseme, ez…® ivem dutuaghr…®zir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa iz…® dam…®.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® suren gumaziba atiatigha men tav an azarazir puvat…®, ‚ÄúN…® tina?‚Äù Me fo, kar Ekiamra.  
\v 13 Egha Iesus avim borogh…®ra ghua egha bret inigha me gan…®di. Egha osiriba sara inigha uaghan me gan…®di.  
\v 14 Dughiar Iesus mozim…®n d…®kavizim…®n g…®n, kar an namba 3…®n dughiam a uab…® isa uan suren gumazibar aka. 
\s1 Iesus Pita m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan sipsipba deraghv…®ra men gan men akuragh 
\p  
\v 15 Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko amegha g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus kamagh…®n Saimon Pitan azai, ‚ÄúSaimon, Jon…®n otarim, n…® ti bar na gifonge, egha n…® na gifongezir arazir kam, a gumazir kaba na gifongezir arazibagh afira?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Pita ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, Ekiam, n…® fo, k…® n…® gifonge.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan gumazamiziba sipsip…®n nguzibar m…®n men akuragh deraghv…®ra men gan.‚Äù\f + \ft (21:15) Gumazir maba Iesus…®n akar kam kamagh a g…®ragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ti bar na gifuegha, egha bizir igharazibagh ifongezir puvat…®?‚Äù Kamagh…®ra gumazir maba uaghan Pitan akar kam g…®ragha ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, guizbang…®ra, n…® fo, k…® n…®n roroam.‚Äù\f* 
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus uam an azara, ‚ÄúSaimon, Jon…®n otarim, n…® ti na gifonge?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Pita a ikara, ‚ÄúAre, Ekiam, n…® fo, k…® n…® gifonge.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan gumazamiziba sipsipbar m…®n men akuragh deraghv…®ra men gan.‚Äù\f + \ft (21:16) Gumazir maba Pitan akar kam kamagh…®n a g…®ragha ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, guizbang…®ra, n…® fo, k…® n…®n roroam.‚Äù\f* 
\v 17 Egha dughiar m…®kezim…®n uam an azara, ‚ÄúSaimon, Jon…®n otarim, n…® ti na gifonge?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Pita Iesus baseme, a dughiar m…®kezim uam an azara ghaze, n…® ti na gifonge? Ez…® a kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® bar bizibagh fo. N…® fo, k…® n…® gifonge.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan gumazamiziba sipsipbar m…®n men akuragh deraghv…®ra men gan.\f + \ft (21:17) Gumazir maba Iesus…®n akar kam kamagh a g…®ragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan roroam?‚Äù Egha Pitan akar kam g…®ragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® fo, k…® n…®n roroam.‚Äù\f* 
\v 18 K…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® fom…®ra igiamra ikia, n…® uab…® letiam uan ivariam ikegha egha danganir n…® mangasa ifongezibagh arui. Ez…® n…® ghurighamin dughiam, n…® uan agharimning feght…®, eght…® gumazir igharazim n…® gikegh n…® inigh…®va danganir n…® mangasa ifongezir puvat…®zim…®n mangam.‚Äù  
\v 19 (Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam m…®g…®a kamagh…®n Pitan aka, a tuavir manam…®n aremegh ziar ekiam God dan…®ngam.) Egha a kamagh…®n Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Suren gumazir Iesus bar ifongezir kam…®n akam 
